var book = {
	"name": "John",
	"numChapters": 21,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">1 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26046A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26046A\"></sup>In the beginning was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26046B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26046B\"></sup>the Word, and the Word was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26046C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26046C\"></sup>with God, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26046D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26046D\"></sup>the Word was God.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>He was in the beginning with God.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26048E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26048E\"></sup>All things came into being through Him, and apart from Him nothing came into being that has come into being.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26049F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26049F\"></sup>In Him was life, and the life was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26049G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26049G\"></sup>the Light of men.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26050H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26050H\"></sup>The Light shines in the darkness, and the darkness did not comprehend it.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>There came a man sent from God, whose name was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26051I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26051I\"></sup>John.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>He came <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26052J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26052J\"></sup>as a witness, to testify about the Light, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26052K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26052K\"></sup>so that all might believe through him.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26053L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26053L\"></sup>He was not the Light, but <i>he came</i> to testify about the Light.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>There was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26054M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26054M\"></sup>the true Light which, coming into the world, enlightens every man.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>He was in the world, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26055N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26055N\"></sup>the world was made through Him, and the world did not know Him.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>He came to His own, and those who were His own did not receive Him.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>But as many as received Him, to them He gave the right to become <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26057O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26057O\"></sup>children of God, <i>even</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26057P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26057P\"></sup>to those who believe in His name,",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26058Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26058Q\"></sup>who were born, not of blood nor of the will of the flesh nor of the will of man, but of God.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26059R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26059R\"></sup>the Word <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26059S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26059S\"></sup>became flesh, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26059T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26059T\"></sup>dwelt among us, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26059U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26059U\"></sup>we saw His glory, glory as of the only begotten from the Father, full of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26059V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26059V\"></sup>grace and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26059W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26059W\"></sup>truth.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>John *<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26060X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26060X\"></sup>testified about Him and cried out, saying, “This was He of whom I said, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26060Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26060Y\"></sup>He who comes after me has a higher rank than I, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26060Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26060Z\"></sup>for He existed before me.’”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>For of His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26061AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26061AA\"></sup>fullness we have all received, and grace upon grace.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26062AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26062AB\"></sup>the Law was given through Moses; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26062AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26062AC\"></sup>grace and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26062AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26062AD\"></sup>truth were realized through Jesus Christ.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26063AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26063AE\"></sup>No one has seen God at any time; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26063AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26063AF\"></sup>the only begotten God who is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26063AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26063AG\"></sup>in the bosom of the Father, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26063AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26063AH\"></sup>He has explained <i>Him</i>.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>This is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26064AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26064AI\"></sup>the testimony of John, when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26064AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26064AJ\"></sup>the Jews sent to him priests and Levites <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26064AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26064AK\"></sup>from Jerusalem to ask him, “Who are you?”",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>And he confessed and did not deny, but confessed, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26065AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26065AL\"></sup>I am not the Christ.”",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>They asked him, “What then? Are you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26066AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26066AM\"></sup>Elijah?” And he *said, “I am not.” “Are you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26066AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26066AN\"></sup>the Prophet?” And he answered, “No.”",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Then they said to him, “Who are you, so that we may give an answer to those who sent us? What do you say about yourself?”",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>He said, “I am <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26068AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26068AO\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">a voice of one crying in the wilderness, ‘Make straight the way of the Lord</span>,’ as Isaiah the prophet said.”",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Now they had been sent from the Pharisees.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>They asked him, and said to him, “Why then are you baptizing, if you are not the Christ, nor Elijah, nor <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26070AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26070AP\"></sup>the Prophet?”",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>John answered them saying, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26071AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26071AQ\"></sup>I baptize in water, <i>but</i> among you stands One whom you do not know.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup><i>It is</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26072AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26072AR\"></sup>He who comes after me, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26072AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26072AS\"></sup>thong of whose sandal I am not worthy to untie.”",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>These things took place in Bethany <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26073AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26073AT\"></sup>beyond the Jordan, where John was baptizing.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>The next day he *saw Jesus coming to him and *said, “Behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26074AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26074AU\"></sup>the Lamb of God who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26074AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26074AV\"></sup>takes away the sin of the world!",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>This is He on behalf of whom I said, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26075AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26075AW\"></sup>After me comes a Man who has a higher rank than I, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26075AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26075AX\"></sup>for He existed before me.’",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>I did not recognize Him, but so that He might be manifested to Israel, I came baptizing in water.”",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>John <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26077AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26077AY\"></sup>testified saying, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26077AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26077AZ\"></sup>I have seen the Spirit descending as a dove out of heaven, and He remained upon Him.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>I did not recognize Him, but He who sent me to baptize in water said to me, ‘He upon whom you see the Spirit descending and remaining upon Him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26078BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26078BA\"></sup>this is the One who baptizes in the Holy Spirit.’",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>I myself have seen, and have testified that this is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26079BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26079BB\"></sup>the Son of God.”",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>Again <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26080BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26080BC\"></sup>the next day John was standing with two of his disciples,",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>and he looked at Jesus as He walked, and *said, “Behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26081BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26081BD\"></sup>the Lamb of God!”",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>The two disciples heard him speak, and they followed Jesus.",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>And Jesus turned and saw them following, and *said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“What do you seek?”</span> They said to Him, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26083BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26083BE\"></sup>Rabbi (which translated means Teacher), where are You staying?”",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>He *said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Come, and you will see.”</span> So they came and saw where He was staying; and they stayed with Him that day, for it was about the tenth hour.",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26085BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26085BF\"></sup>One of the two who heard John <i>speak</i> and followed Him, was Andrew, Simon Peter’s brother.",
			"41": "<sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup>He *found first his own brother Simon and *said to him, “We have found the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26086BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26086BG\"></sup>Messiah” (which translated means Christ).",
			"42": "<sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup>He brought him to Jesus. Jesus looked at him and said, <span class=\"woj\">“You are Simon the son of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26087BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26087BH\"></sup>John; you shall be called <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26087BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26087BI\"></sup>Cephas”</span> (which is translated <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26087BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26087BJ\"></sup>Peter).",
			"43": "<sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26088BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26088BK\"></sup>The next day He purposed to go into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26088BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26088BL\"></sup>Galilee, and He *found <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26088BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26088BM\"></sup>Philip. And Jesus *said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26088BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26088BN\"></sup>Follow Me.”</span>",
			"44": "<sup class=\"versenum\">44 </sup>Now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26089BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26089BO\"></sup>Philip was from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26089BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26089BP\"></sup>Bethsaida, of the city of Andrew and Peter.",
			"45": "<sup class=\"versenum\">45 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26090BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26090BQ\"></sup>Philip *found <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26090BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26090BR\"></sup>Nathanael and *said to him, “We have found Him of whom <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26090BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26090BS\"></sup>Moses in the Law and <i>also</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26090BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26090BT\"></sup>the Prophets wrote—Jesus of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26090BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26090BU\"></sup>Nazareth, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26090BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26090BV\"></sup>the son of Joseph.”",
			"46": "<sup class=\"versenum\">46 </sup>Nathanael said to him, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26091BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26091BW\"></sup>Can any good thing come out of Nazareth?” <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26091BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26091BX\"></sup>Philip *said to him, “Come and see.”",
			"47": "<sup class=\"versenum\">47 </sup>Jesus saw Nathanael coming to Him, and *said of him, <span class=\"woj\">“Behold, an <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26092BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26092BY\"></sup>Israelite indeed, in whom there is no deceit!”</span>",
			"48": "<sup class=\"versenum\">48 </sup>Nathanael *said to Him, “How do You know me?” Jesus answered and said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“Before <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26093BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26093BZ\"></sup>Philip called you, when you were under the fig tree, I saw you.”</span>",
			"49": "<sup class=\"versenum\">49 </sup>Nathanael answered Him, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26094CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26094CA\"></sup>Rabbi, You are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26094CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26094CB\"></sup>the Son of God; You are the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26094CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26094CC\"></sup>King of Israel.”",
			"50": "<sup class=\"versenum\">50 </sup>Jesus answered and said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“Because I said to you that I saw you under the fig tree, do you believe? You will see greater things than these.”</span>",
			"51": "<sup class=\"versenum\">51 </sup>And He *said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“Truly, truly, I say to you, you will see <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26096CD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CD&quot;&gt;CD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26096CD\"></sup>the heavens opened and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26096CE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CE&quot;&gt;CE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26096CE\"></sup>the angels of God ascending and descending on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26096CF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CF&quot;&gt;CF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26096CF\"></sup>the Son of Man.”</span>"
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">2 </span>On <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26097A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26097A\"></sup>the third day there was a wedding in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26097B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26097B\"></sup>Cana of Galilee, and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26097C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26097C\"></sup>mother of Jesus was there;",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>and both Jesus and His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26098D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26098D\"></sup>disciples were invited to the wedding.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>When the wine ran out, the mother of Jesus *said to Him, “They have no wine.”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>And Jesus *said to her, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26100E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26100E\"></sup>Woman, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26100F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26100F\"></sup>what does that have to do with us? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26100G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26100G\"></sup>My hour has not yet come.”</span>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26101H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26101H\"></sup>mother *said to the servants, “Whatever He says to you, do it.”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Now there were six stone waterpots set there <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26102I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26102I\"></sup>for the Jewish custom of purification, containing twenty or thirty gallons each.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Jesus *said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Fill the waterpots with water.”</span> So they filled them up to the brim.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>And He *said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Draw <i>some</i> out now and take it to the headwaiter.”</span> So they took it <i>to him</i>.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>When the headwaiter tasted the water <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26105J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26105J\"></sup>which had become wine, and did not know where it came from (but the servants who had drawn the water knew), the headwaiter *called the bridegroom,",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>and *said to him, “Every man serves the good wine first, and when <i>the people</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26106K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26106K\"></sup>have drunk freely, <i>then he serves</i> the poorer <i>wine; but</i> you have kept the good wine until now.”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>This beginning of <i>His</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26107L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26107L\"></sup>signs Jesus did in Cana of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26107M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26107M\"></sup>Galilee, and manifested His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26107N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26107N\"></sup>glory, and His disciples believed in Him.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>After this He went down to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26108O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26108O\"></sup>Capernaum, He and His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26108P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26108P\"></sup>mother and <i>His</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26108Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26108Q\"></sup>brothers and His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26108R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26108R\"></sup>disciples; and they stayed there a few days.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26109S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26109S\"></sup>The Passover of the Jews was near, and Jesus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26109T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26109T\"></sup>went up to Jerusalem.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26110U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26110U\"></sup>And He found in the temple those who were selling oxen and sheep and doves, and the money changers seated <i>at their tables</i>.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>And He made a scourge of cords, and drove <i>them</i> all out of the temple, with the sheep and the oxen; and He poured out the coins of the money changers and overturned their tables;",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>and to those who were selling <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26112V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26112V\"></sup>the doves He said, <span class=\"woj\">“Take these things away; stop making <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26112W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26112W\"></sup>My Father’s house a place of business.”</span>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26113X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26113X\"></sup>disciples remembered that it was written, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26113Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26113Y\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Zeal for Your house will consume me</span>.”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26114Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26114Z\"></sup>The Jews then said to Him, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26114AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26114AA\"></sup>What sign do You show us as your authority for doing these things?”",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Jesus answered them, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26115AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26115AB\"></sup>Destroy this temple, and in three days I will raise it up.”</span>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26116AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26116AC\"></sup>The Jews then said, “It took <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26116AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26116AD\"></sup>forty-six years to build this temple, and will You raise it up in three days?”",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>But He was speaking of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26117AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26117AE\"></sup>the temple of His body.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>So when He was raised from the dead, His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26118AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26118AF\"></sup>disciples <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26118AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26118AG\"></sup>remembered that He said this; and they believed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26118AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26118AH\"></sup>the Scripture and the word which Jesus had spoken.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Now when He was in Jerusalem at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26119AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26119AI\"></sup>the Passover, during the feast, many believed in His name, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26119AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26119AJ\"></sup>observing His signs which He was doing.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>But Jesus, on His part, was not entrusting Himself to them, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26120AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26120AK\"></sup>He knew all men,",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>and because He did not need anyone to testify concerning man, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26121AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26121AL\"></sup>for He Himself knew what was in man."
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">3 </span>Now there was a man of the Pharisees, named <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26122A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26122A\"></sup>Nicodemus, a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26122B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26122B\"></sup>ruler of the Jews;",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>this man came to Jesus by night and said to Him, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26123C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26123C\"></sup>Rabbi, we know that You have come from God <i>as</i> a teacher; for no one can do these <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26123D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26123D\"></sup>signs that You do unless <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26123E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26123E\"></sup>God is with him.”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Jesus answered and said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“Truly, truly, I say to you, unless one <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26124F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26124F\"></sup>is born again he cannot see <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26124G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26124G\"></sup>the kingdom of God.”</span>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Nicodemus *said to Him, “How can a man be born when he is old? He cannot enter a second time into his mother’s womb and be born, can he?”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Jesus answered, <span class=\"woj\">“Truly, truly, I say to you, unless one is born of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26126H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26126H\"></sup>water and the Spirit he cannot enter into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26126I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26126I\"></sup>the kingdom of God.</span>",
			"6": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26127J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26127J\"></sup>That which is born of the flesh is flesh, and that which is born of the Spirit is spirit.</span>",
			"7": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Do not be amazed that I said to you, ‘You must be born again.’</span>",
			"8": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26129K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26129K\"></sup>The wind blows where it wishes and you hear the sound of it, but do not know where it comes from and where it is going; so is everyone who is born of the Spirit.”</span>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Nicodemus said to Him, “How can these things be?”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Jesus answered and said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“Are you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26131L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26131L\"></sup>the teacher of Israel and do not understand these things?</span>",
			"11": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Truly, truly, I say to you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26132M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26132M\"></sup>we speak of what we know and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26132N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26132N\"></sup>testify of what we have seen, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26132O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26132O\"></sup>you do not accept our testimony.</span>",
			"12": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>If I told you earthly things and you do not believe, how will you believe if I tell you heavenly things?</span>",
			"13": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26134P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26134P\"></sup>No one has ascended into heaven, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26134Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26134Q\"></sup>He who descended from heaven: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26134R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26134R\"></sup>the Son of Man.</span>",
			"14": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>As <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26135S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26135S\"></sup>Moses lifted up the serpent in the wilderness, even so must <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26135T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26135T\"></sup>the Son of Man <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26135U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26135U\"></sup>be lifted up;</span>",
			"15": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>so that whoever believes will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26136V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26136V\"></sup>in Him have eternal life.</span>",
			"16": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“For God so <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26137W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26137W\"></sup>loved the world, that He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26137X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26137X\"></sup>gave His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26137Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26137Y\"></sup>only begotten Son, that whoever <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26137Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26137Z\"></sup>believes in Him shall not perish, but have eternal life.</span>",
			"17": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>For God <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26138AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26138AA\"></sup>did not send the Son into the world <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26138AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26138AB\"></sup>to judge the world, but that the world might be saved through Him.</span>",
			"18": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26139AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26139AC\"></sup>He who believes in Him is not judged; he who does not believe has been judged already, because he has not believed in the name of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26139AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26139AD\"></sup>the only begotten Son of God.</span>",
			"19": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>This is the judgment, that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26140AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26140AE\"></sup>the Light has come into the world, and men loved the darkness rather than the Light, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26140AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26140AF\"></sup>their deeds were evil.</span>",
			"20": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26141AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26141AG\"></sup>For everyone who does evil hates the Light, and does not come to the Light for fear that his deeds will be exposed.</span>",
			"21": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>But he who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26142AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26142AH\"></sup>practices the truth comes to the Light, so that his deeds may be manifested as having been wrought in God.”</span>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>After these things Jesus and His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26143AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26143AI\"></sup>disciples came into the land of Judea, and there He was spending time with them and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26143AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26143AJ\"></sup>baptizing.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>John also was baptizing in Aenon near Salim, because there was much water there; and <i>people</i> were coming and were being baptized—",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26145AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26145AK\"></sup>John had not yet been thrown into prison.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Therefore there arose a discussion on the part of John’s disciples with a Jew about <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26146AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26146AL\"></sup>purification.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>And they came to John and said to him, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26147AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26147AM\"></sup>Rabbi, He who was with you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26147AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26147AN\"></sup>beyond the Jordan, to whom you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26147AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26147AO\"></sup>have testified, behold, He is baptizing and all are coming to Him.”",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>John answered and said, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26148AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26148AP\"></sup>A man can receive nothing unless it <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26148AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26148AQ\"></sup>has been given him from heaven.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>You yourselves are my witnesses that I said, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26149AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26149AR\"></sup>I am not the Christ,’ but, ‘I have been sent ahead of Him.’",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>He who has the bride is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26150AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26150AS\"></sup>the bridegroom; but the friend of the bridegroom, who stands and hears him, rejoices greatly because of the bridegroom’s voice. So this <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26150AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26150AT\"></sup>joy of mine has been made full.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>He must increase, but I must decrease.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26152AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26152AU\"></sup>He who comes from above is above all, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26152AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26152AV\"></sup>he who is of the earth is from the earth and speaks of the earth. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26152AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26152AW\"></sup>He who comes from heaven is above all.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>What He has seen and heard, of that He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26153AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26153AX\"></sup>testifies; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26153AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26153AY\"></sup>no one receives His testimony.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>He who has received His testimony <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26154AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26154AZ\"></sup>has set his seal to <i>this</i>, that God is true.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>For He whom God has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26155BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26155BA\"></sup>sent speaks the words of God; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26155BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26155BB\"></sup>for He gives the Spirit without measure.",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26156BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26156BC\"></sup>The Father loves the Son and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26156BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26156BD\"></sup>has given all things into His hand.",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>He who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26157BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26157BE\"></sup>believes in the Son has eternal life; but he who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26157BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26157BF\"></sup>does not obey the Son will not see life, but the wrath of God abides on him.”"
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">4 </span>Therefore when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26158A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26158A\"></sup>the Lord knew that the Pharisees had heard that Jesus was making and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26158B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26158B\"></sup>baptizing more disciples than John",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>(although <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26159C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26159C\"></sup>Jesus Himself was not baptizing, but His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26159D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26159D\"></sup>disciples were),",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>He left <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26160E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26160E\"></sup>Judea and went away <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26160F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26160F\"></sup>again into Galilee.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>And He had to pass through <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26161G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26161G\"></sup>Samaria.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>So He *came to a city of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26162H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26162H\"></sup>Samaria called Sychar, near <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26162I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26162I\"></sup>the parcel of ground that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26162J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26162J\"></sup>Jacob gave to his son Joseph;",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>and Jacob’s well was there. So Jesus, being wearied from His journey, was sitting thus by the well. It was about the sixth hour.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>There *came a woman of Samaria to draw water. Jesus *said to her, <span class=\"woj\">“Give Me a drink.”</span>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>For His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26165K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26165K\"></sup>disciples had gone away into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26165L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26165L\"></sup>the city to buy food.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Therefore the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26166M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26166M\"></sup>Samaritan woman *said to Him, “How is it that You, being a Jew, ask me for a drink since I am a Samaritan woman?” (For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26166N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26166N\"></sup>Jews have no dealings with Samaritans.)",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Jesus answered and said to her, <span class=\"woj\">“If you knew the gift of God, and who it is who says to you, ‘Give Me a drink,’ you would have asked Him, and He would have given you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26167O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26167O\"></sup>living water.”</span>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>She *said to Him, “Sir, You have nothing to draw with and the well is deep; where then do You get that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26168P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26168P\"></sup>living water?",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>You are not greater than our father Jacob, are You, who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26169Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26169Q\"></sup>gave us the well, and drank of it himself and his sons and his cattle?”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Jesus answered and said to her, <span class=\"woj\">“Everyone who drinks of this water will thirst again;</span>",
			"14": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>but whoever drinks of the water that I will give him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26171R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26171R\"></sup>shall never thirst; but the water that I will give him will become in him a well of water springing up to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26171S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26171S\"></sup>eternal life.”</span>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>The woman *said to Him, “Sir, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26172T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26172T\"></sup>give me this water, so I will not be thirsty nor come all the way here to draw.”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>He *said to her, <span class=\"woj\">“Go, call your husband and come here.”</span>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>The woman answered and said, “I have no husband.” Jesus *said to her, <span class=\"woj\">“You have correctly said, ‘I have no husband’;</span>",
			"18": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>for you have had five husbands, and the one whom you now have is not your husband; this you have said truly.”</span>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>The woman *said to Him, “Sir, I perceive that You are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26176U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26176U\"></sup>a prophet.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26177V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26177V\"></sup>Our fathers worshiped in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26177W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26177W\"></sup>this mountain, and you <i>people</i> say that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26177X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26177X\"></sup>in Jerusalem is the place where men ought to worship.”",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Jesus *said to her, <span class=\"woj\">“Woman, believe Me, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26178Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26178Y\"></sup>an hour is coming when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26178Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26178Z\"></sup>neither in this mountain nor in Jerusalem will you worship the Father.</span>",
			"22": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26179AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26179AA\"></sup>You worship what you do not know; we worship what we know, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26179AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26179AB\"></sup>salvation is from the Jews.</span>",
			"23": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26180AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26180AC\"></sup>an hour is coming, and now is, when the true worshipers will worship the Father <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26180AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26180AD\"></sup>in spirit and truth; for such people the Father seeks to be His worshipers.</span>",
			"24": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>God is spirit, and those who worship Him must worship <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26181AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26181AE\"></sup>in spirit and truth.”</span>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>The woman *said to Him, “I know that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26182AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26182AF\"></sup>Messiah is coming (<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26182AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26182AG\"></sup>He who is called Christ); when that One comes, He will declare all things to us.”",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Jesus *said to her, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26183AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26183AH\"></sup>I who speak to you am <i>He</i>.”</span>",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>At this point His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26184AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26184AI\"></sup>disciples came, and they were amazed that He had been speaking with a woman, yet no one said, “What do You seek?” or, “Why do You speak with her?”",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>So the woman left her waterpot, and went into the city and *said to the men,",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>“Come, see a man <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26186AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26186AJ\"></sup>who told me all the things that I <i>have</i> done; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26186AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26186AK\"></sup>this is not the Christ, is it?”",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>They went out of the city, and were coming to Him.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>Meanwhile the disciples were urging Him, saying, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26188AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26188AL\"></sup>Rabbi, eat.”",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>But He said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“I have food to eat that you do not know about.”</span>",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>So the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26190AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26190AM\"></sup>disciples were saying to one another, “No one brought Him <i>anything</i> to eat, did he?”",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>Jesus *said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“My food is to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26191AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26191AN\"></sup>do the will of Him who sent Me and to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26191AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26191AO\"></sup>accomplish His work.</span>",
			"35": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>Do you not say, ‘There are yet four months, and <i>then</i> comes the harvest’? Behold, I say to you, lift up your eyes and look on the fields, that they are white <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26192AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26192AP\"></sup>for harvest.</span>",
			"36": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>Already he who reaps is receiving <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26193AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26193AQ\"></sup>wages and is gathering <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26193AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26193AR\"></sup>fruit for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26193AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26193AS\"></sup>life eternal; so that he who sows and he who reaps may rejoice together.</span>",
			"37": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>For in this <i>case</i> the saying is true, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26194AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26194AT\"></sup>One sows and another reaps.’</span>",
			"38": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>I sent you to reap that for which you have not labored; others have labored and you have entered into their labor.”</span>",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>From <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26196AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26196AU\"></sup>that city many of the Samaritans believed in Him because of the word of the woman who testified, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26196AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26196AV\"></sup>He told me all the things that I <i>have</i> done.”",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>So when the Samaritans came to Jesus, they were asking Him to stay with them; and He stayed there two days.",
			"41": "<sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup>Many more believed because of His word;",
			"42": "<sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup>and they were saying to the woman, “It is no longer because of what you said that we believe, for we have heard for ourselves and know that this One is indeed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26199AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26199AW\"></sup>the Savior of the world.”",
			"43": "<sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup>After <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26200AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26200AX\"></sup>the two days He went forth from there into Galilee.",
			"44": "<sup class=\"versenum\">44 </sup>For Jesus Himself testified that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26201AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26201AY\"></sup>a prophet has no honor in his own country.",
			"45": "<sup class=\"versenum\">45 </sup>So when He came to Galilee, the Galileans received Him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26202AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26202AZ\"></sup>having seen all the things that He did in Jerusalem at the feast; for they themselves also went to the feast.",
			"46": "<sup class=\"versenum\">46 </sup>Therefore He came again to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26203BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26203BA\"></sup>Cana of Galilee <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26203BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26203BB\"></sup>where He had made the water wine. And there was a royal official whose son was sick at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26203BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26203BC\"></sup>Capernaum.",
			"47": "<sup class=\"versenum\">47 </sup>When he heard that Jesus had come <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26204BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26204BD\"></sup>out of Judea into Galilee, he went to Him and was imploring <i>Him</i> to come down and heal his son; for he was at the point of death.",
			"48": "<sup class=\"versenum\">48 </sup>So Jesus said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“Unless you <i>people</i> see <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26205BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26205BE\"></sup>signs and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26205BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26205BF\"></sup>wonders, you <i>simply</i> will not believe.”</span>",
			"49": "<sup class=\"versenum\">49 </sup>The royal official *said to Him, “Sir, come down before my child dies.”",
			"50": "<sup class=\"versenum\">50 </sup>Jesus *said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26207BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26207BG\"></sup>Go; your son lives.”</span> The man believed the word that Jesus spoke to him and started off.",
			"51": "<sup class=\"versenum\">51 </sup>As he was now going down, <i>his</i> slaves met him, saying that his son was living.",
			"52": "<sup class=\"versenum\">52 </sup>So he inquired of them the hour when he began to get better. Then they said to him, “Yesterday at the seventh hour the fever left him.”",
			"53": "<sup class=\"versenum\">53 </sup>So the father knew that <i>it was</i> at that hour in which Jesus said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“Your son lives”</span>; and he himself believed and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26210BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26210BH\"></sup>his whole household.",
			"54": "<sup class=\"versenum\">54 </sup>This is again a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26211BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26211BI\"></sup>second sign that Jesus performed when He had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26211BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26211BJ\"></sup>come out of Judea into Galilee."
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">5 </span>After these things there was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26212A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26212A\"></sup>a feast of the Jews, and Jesus went up to Jerusalem.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Now there is in Jerusalem by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26213B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26213B\"></sup>the sheep <i>gate</i> a pool, which is called <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26213C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26213C\"></sup>in Hebrew Bethesda, having five porticoes.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>In these lay a multitude of those who were sick, blind, lame, and withered, [waiting for the moving of the waters;",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>for an angel of the Lord went down at certain seasons into the pool and stirred up the water; whoever then first, after the stirring up of the water, stepped in was made well from whatever disease with which he was afflicted.]",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>A man was there who had been ill for thirty-eight years.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>When Jesus saw him lying <i>there</i>, and knew that he had already been a long time <i>in that condition</i>, He *said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“Do you wish to get well?”</span>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>The sick man answered Him, “Sir, I have no man to put me into the pool when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26218D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26218D\"></sup>the water is stirred up, but while I am coming, another steps down before me.”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Jesus *said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26219E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26219E\"></sup>Get up, pick up your pallet and walk.”</span>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Immediately the man became well, and picked up his pallet and <i>began</i> to walk.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26220F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26220F\"></sup>Now it was the Sabbath on that day.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>So <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26221G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26221G\"></sup>the Jews were saying to the man who was cured, “It is the Sabbath, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26221H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26221H\"></sup>it is not permissible for you to carry your pallet.”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>But he answered them, “He who made me well was the one who said to me, <span class=\"woj\">‘Pick up your pallet and walk.’</span>”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>They asked him, “Who is the man who said to you, <span class=\"woj\">‘Pick up <i>your pallet</i> and walk’</span>?”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>But the man who was healed did not know who it was, for Jesus had slipped away while there was a crowd in <i>that</i> place.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Afterward Jesus *found him in the temple and said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“Behold, you have become well; do not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26225I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26225I\"></sup>sin anymore, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26225J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26225J\"></sup>so that nothing worse happens to you.”</span>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>The man went away, and told <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26226K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26226K\"></sup>the Jews that it was Jesus who had made him well.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>For this reason <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26227L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26227L\"></sup>the Jews were persecuting Jesus, because He was doing these things on the Sabbath.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>But He answered them, <span class=\"woj\">“My Father is working until now, and I Myself am working.”</span>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>For this reason therefore <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26229M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26229M\"></sup>the Jews <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26229N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26229N\"></sup>were seeking all the more to kill Him, because He not only was breaking the Sabbath, but also was calling God His own Father, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26229O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26229O\"></sup>making Himself equal with God.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Therefore Jesus answered and was saying to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Truly, truly, I say to you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26230P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26230P\"></sup>the Son can do nothing of Himself, unless <i>it is</i> something He sees the Father doing; for whatever the Father does, these things the Son also does in like manner.</span>",
			"20": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26231Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26231Q\"></sup>For the Father loves the Son, and shows Him all things that He Himself is doing; and <i>the Father</i> will show Him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26231R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26231R\"></sup>greater works than these, so that you will marvel.</span>",
			"21": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>For just as the Father raises the dead and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26232S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26232S\"></sup>gives them life, even so <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26232T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26232T\"></sup>the Son also gives life to whom He wishes.</span>",
			"22": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>For not even the Father judges anyone, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26233U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26233U\"></sup>He has given all judgment to the Son,</span>",
			"23": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>so that all will honor the Son even as they honor the Father. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26234V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26234V\"></sup>He who does not honor the Son does not honor the Father who sent Him.</span>",
			"24": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>“Truly, truly, I say to you, he who hears My word, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26235W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26235W\"></sup>believes Him who sent Me, has eternal life, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26235X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26235X\"></sup>does not come into judgment, but has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26235Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26235Y\"></sup>passed out of death into life.</span>",
			"25": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Truly, truly, I say to you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26236Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26236Z\"></sup>an hour is coming and now is, when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26236AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26236AA\"></sup>the dead will hear the voice of the Son of God, and those who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26236AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26236AB\"></sup>hear will live.</span>",
			"26": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>For just as the Father has life in Himself, even so He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26237AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26237AC\"></sup>gave to the Son also to have life in Himself;</span>",
			"27": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>and He gave Him authority to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26238AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26238AD\"></sup>execute judgment, because He is <i>the</i> Son of Man.</span>",
			"28": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Do not marvel at this; for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26239AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26239AE\"></sup>an hour is coming, in which <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26239AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26239AF\"></sup>all who are in the tombs will hear His voice,</span>",
			"29": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>and will come forth; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26240AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26240AG\"></sup>those who did the good <i>deeds</i> to a resurrection of life, those who committed the evil <i>deeds</i> to a resurrection of judgment.</span>",
			"30": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26241AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26241AH\"></sup>I can do nothing on My own initiative. As I hear, I judge; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26241AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26241AI\"></sup>My judgment is just, because I do not seek My own will, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26241AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26241AJ\"></sup>the will of Him who sent Me.</span>",
			"31": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26242AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26242AK\"></sup>If I <i>alone</i> testify about Myself, My testimony is not true.</span>",
			"32": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>There is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26243AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26243AL\"></sup>another who testifies of Me, and I know that the testimony which He gives about Me is true.</span>",
			"33": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>You have sent to John, and he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26244AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26244AM\"></sup>has testified to the truth.</span>",
			"34": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26245AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26245AN\"></sup>the testimony which I receive is not from man, but I say these things so that you may be saved.</span>",
			"35": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>He was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26246AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26246AO\"></sup>the lamp that was burning and was shining and you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26246AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26246AP\"></sup>were willing to rejoice for a while in his light.</span>",
			"36": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>But the testimony which I have is greater than <i>the testimony of</i> John; for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26247AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26247AQ\"></sup>the works which the Father has given Me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26247AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26247AR\"></sup>to accomplish—the very works that I do—testify about Me, that the Father <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26247AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26247AS\"></sup>has sent Me.</span>",
			"37": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>And the Father who sent Me, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26248AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26248AT\"></sup>He has testified of Me. You have neither heard His voice at any time nor seen His form.</span>",
			"38": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>You do not have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26249AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26249AU\"></sup>His word abiding in you, for you do not believe Him whom He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26249AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26249AV\"></sup>sent.</span>",
			"39": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26250AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26250AW\"></sup>You search the Scriptures because you think that in them you have eternal life; it is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26250AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26250AX\"></sup>these that testify about Me;</span>",
			"40": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>and you are unwilling to come to Me so that you may have life.</span>",
			"41": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26252AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26252AY\"></sup>I do not receive glory from men;</span>",
			"42": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup>but I know you, that you do not have the love of God in yourselves.</span>",
			"43": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup>I have come in My Father’s name, and you do not receive Me; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26254AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26254AZ\"></sup>if another comes in his own name, you will receive him.</span>",
			"44": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">44 </sup>How can you believe, when you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26255BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26255BA\"></sup>receive glory from one another and you do not seek <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26255BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26255BB\"></sup>the glory that is from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26255BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26255BC\"></sup>the <i>one and</i> only God?</span>",
			"45": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">45 </sup>Do not think that I will accuse you before the Father; the one who accuses you is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26256BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26256BD\"></sup>Moses, in whom you have set your hope.</span>",
			"46": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">46 </sup>For if you believed Moses, you would believe Me, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26257BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26257BE\"></sup>he wrote about Me.</span>",
			"47": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">47 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26258BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26258BF\"></sup>if you do not believe his writings, how will you believe My words?”</span>"
		},
		"6": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">6 </span>After these things <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26259A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26259A\"></sup>Jesus went away to the other side of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26259B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26259B\"></sup>the Sea of Galilee (or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26259C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26259C\"></sup>Tiberias).",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>A large crowd followed Him, because they saw the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26260D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26260D\"></sup>signs which He was performing on those who were sick.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26261E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26261E\"></sup>Jesus went up on the mountain, and there He sat down with His disciples.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26262F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26262F\"></sup>the Passover, the feast of the Jews, was near.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Therefore Jesus, lifting up His eyes and seeing that a large crowd was coming to Him, *said to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26263G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26263G\"></sup>Philip, <span class=\"woj\">“Where are we to buy bread, so that these may eat?”</span>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>This He was saying to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26264H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26264H\"></sup>test him, for He Himself knew what He was intending to do.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26265I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26265I\"></sup>Philip answered Him, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26265J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26265J\"></sup>Two hundred denarii worth of bread is not sufficient for them, for everyone to receive a little.”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>One of His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26266K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26266K\"></sup>disciples, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26266L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26266L\"></sup>Andrew, Simon Peter’s brother, *said to Him,",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“There is a lad here who has five barley loaves and two <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26267M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26267M\"></sup>fish, but what are these for so many people?”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Jesus said, <span class=\"woj\">“Have the people sit down.”</span> Now there was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26268N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26268N\"></sup>much grass in the place. So the men sat down, in number about <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26268O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26268O\"></sup>five thousand.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Jesus then took the loaves, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26269P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26269P\"></sup>having given thanks, He distributed to those who were seated; likewise also of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26269Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26269Q\"></sup>fish as much as they wanted.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>When they were filled, He *said to His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26270R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26270R\"></sup>disciples, <span class=\"woj\">“Gather up the leftover fragments so that nothing will be lost.”</span>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>So they gathered them up, and filled twelve <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26271S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26271S\"></sup>baskets with fragments from the five barley loaves which were left over by those who had eaten.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Therefore when the people saw the sign which He had performed, they said, “This is truly the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26272T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26272T\"></sup>Prophet who is to come into the world.”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>So Jesus, perceiving that they were intending to come and take Him by force <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26273U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26273U\"></sup>to make Him king, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26273V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26273V\"></sup>withdrew again to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26273W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26273W\"></sup>the mountain by Himself alone.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Now when evening came, His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26274X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26274X\"></sup>disciples went down to the sea,",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>and after getting into a boat, they <i>started to</i> cross the sea <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26275Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26275Y\"></sup>to Capernaum. It had already become dark, and Jesus had not yet come to them.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>The sea <i>began</i> to be stirred up because a strong wind was blowing.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Then, when they had rowed about three or four miles, they *saw Jesus walking on the sea and drawing near to the boat; and they were frightened.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>But He *said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“It is I; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26278Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26278Z\"></sup>do not be afraid.”</span>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>So they were willing to receive Him into the boat, and immediately the boat was at the land to which they were going.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>The next day <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26280AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26280AA\"></sup>the crowd that stood on the other side of the sea saw that there was no other small boat there, except one, and that Jesus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26280AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26280AB\"></sup>had not entered with His disciples into the boat, but <i>that</i> His disciples had gone away alone.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>There came other small boats from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26281AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26281AC\"></sup>Tiberias near to the place where they ate the bread after the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26281AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26281AD\"></sup>Lord <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26281AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26281AE\"></sup>had given thanks.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>So when the crowd saw that Jesus was not there, nor His disciples, they themselves got into the small boats, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26282AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26282AF\"></sup>came to Capernaum seeking Jesus.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>When they found Him on the other side of the sea, they said to Him, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26283AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26283AG\"></sup>Rabbi, when did You get here?”",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Jesus answered them and said, <span class=\"woj\">“Truly, truly, I say to you, you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26284AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26284AH\"></sup>seek Me, not because you saw <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26284AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26284AI\"></sup>signs, but because you ate of the loaves and were filled.</span>",
			"27": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Do not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26285AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26285AJ\"></sup>work for the food which perishes, but for the food which endures to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26285AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26285AK\"></sup>eternal life, which <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26285AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26285AL\"></sup>the Son of Man will give to you, for on Him the Father, God, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26285AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26285AM\"></sup>has set His seal.”</span>",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Therefore they said to Him, “What shall we do, so that we may work the works of God?”",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>Jesus answered and said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“This is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26287AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26287AN\"></sup>the work of God, that you believe in Him whom He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26287AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26287AO\"></sup>has sent.”</span>",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>So they said to Him, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26288AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26288AP\"></sup>What then do You do for a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26288AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26288AQ\"></sup>sign, so that we may see, and believe You? What work do You perform?",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26289AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26289AR\"></sup>Our fathers ate the manna in the wilderness; as it is written, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26289AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26289AS\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">He gave them bread out of heaven to eat</span>.’”",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>Jesus then said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Truly, truly, I say to you, it is not Moses who has given you the bread out of heaven, but it is My Father who gives you the true bread out of heaven.</span>",
			"33": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>For the bread of God is that which <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26291AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26291AT\"></sup>comes down out of heaven, and gives life to the world.”</span>",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>Then they said to Him, “Lord, always <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26292AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26292AU\"></sup>give us this bread.”",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>Jesus said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26293AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26293AV\"></sup>I am the bread of life; he who comes to Me will not hunger, and he who believes in Me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26293AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26293AW\"></sup>will never thirst.</span>",
			"36": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26294AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26294AX\"></sup>I said to you that you have seen Me, and yet do not believe.</span>",
			"37": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26295AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26295AY\"></sup>All that the Father gives Me will come to Me, and the one who comes to Me I will certainly not cast out.</span>",
			"38": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26296AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26296AZ\"></sup>I have come down from heaven, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26296BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26296BA\"></sup>not to do My own will, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26296BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26296BB\"></sup>the will of Him who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26296BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26296BC\"></sup>sent Me.</span>",
			"39": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>This is the will of Him who sent Me, that of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26297BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26297BD\"></sup>all that He has given Me I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26297BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26297BE\"></sup>lose nothing, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26297BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26297BF\"></sup>raise it up on the last day.</span>",
			"40": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>For this is the will of My Father, that everyone who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26298BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26298BG\"></sup>beholds the Son and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26298BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26298BH\"></sup>believes in Him will have eternal life, and I Myself will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26298BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26298BI\"></sup>raise him up on the last day.”</span>",
			"41": "<sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26299BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26299BJ\"></sup>Therefore the Jews were grumbling about Him, because He said, <span class=\"woj\">“I am the bread that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26299BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26299BK\"></sup>came down out of heaven.”</span>",
			"42": "<sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup>They were saying, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26300BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26300BL\"></sup>Is not this Jesus, the son of Joseph, whose father and mother <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26300BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26300BM\"></sup>we know? How does He now say, <span class=\"woj\">‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26300BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26300BN\"></sup>I have come down out of heaven’</span>?”",
			"43": "<sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup>Jesus answered and said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Do not grumble among yourselves.</span>",
			"44": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">44 </sup>No one can come to Me unless the Father who sent Me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26302BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26302BO\"></sup>draws him; and I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26302BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26302BP\"></sup>raise him up on the last day.</span>",
			"45": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">45 </sup>It is written <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26303BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26303BQ\"></sup>in the prophets, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26303BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26303BR\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">And they shall all be</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26303BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26303BS\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">taught of God</span>.’ Everyone who has heard and learned from the Father, comes to Me.</span>",
			"46": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">46 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26304BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26304BT\"></sup>Not that anyone has seen the Father, except the One who is from God; He has seen the Father.</span>",
			"47": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">47 </sup>Truly, truly, I say to you, he who believes <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26305BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26305BU\"></sup>has eternal life.</span>",
			"48": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">48 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26306BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26306BV\"></sup>I am the bread of life.</span>",
			"49": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">49 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26307BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26307BW\"></sup>Your fathers ate the manna in the wilderness, and they died.</span>",
			"50": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">50 </sup>This is the bread which <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26308BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26308BX\"></sup>comes down out of heaven, so that one may eat of it and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26308BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26308BY\"></sup>not die.</span>",
			"51": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">51 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26309BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26309BZ\"></sup>I am the living bread that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26309CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26309CA\"></sup>came down out of heaven; if anyone eats of this bread, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26309CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26309CB\"></sup>he will live forever; and the bread also which I will give <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26309CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26309CC\"></sup>for the life of the world is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26309CD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CD&quot;&gt;CD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26309CD\"></sup>My flesh.”</span>",
			"52": "<sup class=\"versenum\">52 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26310CE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CE&quot;&gt;CE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26310CE\"></sup>Then the Jews <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26310CF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CF&quot;&gt;CF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26310CF\"></sup><i>began</i> to argue with one another, saying, “How can this man give us <i>His</i> flesh to eat?”",
			"53": "<sup class=\"versenum\">53 </sup>So Jesus said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Truly, truly, I say to you, unless you eat the flesh of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26311CG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CG&quot;&gt;CG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26311CG\"></sup>the Son of Man and drink His blood, you have no life in yourselves.</span>",
			"54": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">54 </sup>He who eats My flesh and drinks My blood has eternal life, and I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26312CH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CH&quot;&gt;CH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26312CH\"></sup>raise him up on the last day.</span>",
			"55": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">55 </sup>For My flesh is true food, and My blood is true drink.</span>",
			"56": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">56 </sup>He who eats My flesh and drinks My blood <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26314CI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CI&quot;&gt;CI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26314CI\"></sup>abides in Me, and I in him.</span>",
			"57": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">57 </sup>As the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26315CJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CJ&quot;&gt;CJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26315CJ\"></sup>living Father <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26315CK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CK&quot;&gt;CK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26315CK\"></sup>sent Me, and I live because of the Father, so he who eats Me, he also will live because of Me.</span>",
			"58": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">58 </sup>This is the bread which <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26316CL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CL&quot;&gt;CL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26316CL\"></sup>came down out of heaven; not as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26316CM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CM&quot;&gt;CM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26316CM\"></sup>the fathers ate and died; he who eats this bread <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26316CN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CN&quot;&gt;CN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26316CN\"></sup>will live forever.”</span>",
			"59": "<sup class=\"versenum\">59 </sup>These things He said <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26317CO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CO&quot;&gt;CO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26317CO\"></sup>in the synagogue as He taught <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26317CP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CP&quot;&gt;CP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26317CP\"></sup>in Capernaum.",
			"60": "<sup class=\"versenum\">60 </sup>Therefore many of His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26318CQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CQ&quot;&gt;CQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26318CQ\"></sup>disciples, when they heard <i>this</i> said, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26318CR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CR&quot;&gt;CR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26318CR\"></sup>This is a difficult statement; who can listen to it?”",
			"61": "<sup class=\"versenum\">61 </sup>But Jesus, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26319CS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CS&quot;&gt;CS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26319CS\"></sup>conscious that His disciples grumbled at this, said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Does this <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26319CT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CT&quot;&gt;CT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26319CT\"></sup>cause you to stumble?</span>",
			"62": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">62 </sup><i>What</i> then if you see <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26320CU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CU&quot;&gt;CU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26320CU\"></sup>the Son of Man <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26320CV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CV&quot;&gt;CV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26320CV\"></sup>ascending to where He was before?</span>",
			"63": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">63 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26321CW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CW&quot;&gt;CW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26321CW\"></sup>It is the Spirit who gives life; the flesh profits nothing; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26321CX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CX&quot;&gt;CX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26321CX\"></sup>the words that I have spoken to you are spirit and are life.</span>",
			"64": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">64 </sup>But there are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26322CY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CY&quot;&gt;CY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26322CY\"></sup>some of you who do not believe.”</span> For Jesus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26322CZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CZ&quot;&gt;CZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26322CZ\"></sup>knew from the beginning who they were who did not believe, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26322DA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DA&quot;&gt;DA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26322DA\"></sup>who it was that would betray Him.",
			"65": "<sup class=\"versenum\">65 </sup>And He was saying, <span class=\"woj\">“For this reason I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26323DB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DB&quot;&gt;DB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26323DB\"></sup>said to you, that no one can come to Me unless <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26323DC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DC&quot;&gt;DC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26323DC\"></sup>it has been granted him from the Father.”</span>",
			"66": "<sup class=\"versenum\">66 </sup>As a result of this many of His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26324DD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DD&quot;&gt;DD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26324DD\"></sup>disciples <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26324DE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DE&quot;&gt;DE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26324DE\"></sup>withdrew and were not walking with Him anymore.",
			"67": "<sup class=\"versenum\">67 </sup>So Jesus said to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26325DF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DF&quot;&gt;DF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26325DF\"></sup>the twelve, <span class=\"woj\">“You do not want to go away also, do you?”</span>",
			"68": "<sup class=\"versenum\">68 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26326DG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DG&quot;&gt;DG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26326DG\"></sup>Simon Peter answered Him, “Lord, to whom shall we go? You have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26326DH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DH&quot;&gt;DH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26326DH\"></sup>words of eternal life.",
			"69": "<sup class=\"versenum\">69 </sup>We have believed and have come to know that You are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26327DI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DI&quot;&gt;DI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26327DI\"></sup>the Holy One of God.”",
			"70": "<sup class=\"versenum\">70 </sup>Jesus answered them, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26328DJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DJ&quot;&gt;DJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26328DJ\"></sup>Did I Myself not choose you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26328DK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DK&quot;&gt;DK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26328DK\"></sup>the twelve, and <i>yet</i> one of you is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26328DL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DL&quot;&gt;DL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26328DL\"></sup>a devil?”</span>",
			"71": "<sup class=\"versenum\">71 </sup>Now He meant Judas <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26329DM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DM&quot;&gt;DM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26329DM\"></sup><i>the son</i> of Simon Iscariot, for he, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26329DN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DN&quot;&gt;DN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26329DN\"></sup>one of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26329DO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DO&quot;&gt;DO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26329DO\"></sup>the twelve, was going to betray Him."
		},
		"7": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">7 </span>After these things Jesus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26330A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26330A\"></sup>was walking in Galilee, for He was unwilling to walk in Judea because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26330B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26330B\"></sup>the Jews <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26330C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26330C\"></sup>were seeking to kill Him.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Now the feast of the Jews, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26331D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26331D\"></sup>the Feast of Booths, was near.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Therefore His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26332E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26332E\"></sup>brothers said to Him, “Leave here and go into Judea, so that Your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26332F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26332F\"></sup>disciples also may see Your works which You are doing.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>For no one does anything in secret when he himself seeks to be <i>known</i> publicly. If You do these things, show Yourself to the world.”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>For not even His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26334G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26334G\"></sup>brothers were believing in Him.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>So Jesus *said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26335H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26335H\"></sup>My time is not yet here, but your time is always opportune.</span>",
			"7": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26336I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26336I\"></sup>The world cannot hate you, but it hates Me because I testify of it, that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26336J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26336J\"></sup>its deeds are evil.</span>",
			"8": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Go up to the feast yourselves; I do not go up to this feast because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26337K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26337K\"></sup>My time has not yet fully come.”</span>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Having said these things to them, He stayed in Galilee.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>But when His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26339L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26339L\"></sup>brothers had gone up to the feast, then He Himself also went up, not publicly, but as if, in secret.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26340M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26340M\"></sup>So the Jews <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26340N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26340N\"></sup>were seeking Him at the feast and were saying, “Where is He?”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>There was much grumbling among the crowds concerning Him; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26341O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26341O\"></sup>some were saying, “He is a good man”; others were saying, “No, on the contrary, He leads the people astray.”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Yet no one was speaking openly of Him for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26342P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26342P\"></sup>fear of the Jews.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>But when it was now the midst of the feast Jesus went up into the temple, and <i>began to</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26343Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26343Q\"></sup>teach.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26344R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26344R\"></sup>The Jews then were astonished, saying, “How has this man <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26344S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26344S\"></sup>become learned, having never been educated?”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>So Jesus answered them and said, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26345T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26345T\"></sup>My teaching is not Mine, but His who sent Me.</span>",
			"17": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26346U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26346U\"></sup>If anyone is willing to do His will, he will know of the teaching, whether it is of God or <i>whether</i> I speak from Myself.</span>",
			"18": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>He who speaks from himself <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26347V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26347V\"></sup>seeks his own glory; but He who is seeking the glory of the One who sent Him, He is true, and there is no unrighteousness in Him.</span>",
			"19": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26348W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26348W\"></sup>Did not Moses give you the Law, and <i>yet</i> none of you carries out the Law? Why do you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26348X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26348X\"></sup>seek to kill Me?”</span>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>The crowd answered, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26349Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26349Y\"></sup>You have a demon! Who seeks to kill You?”",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Jesus answered them, <span class=\"woj\">“I did <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26350Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26350Z\"></sup>one deed, and you all marvel.</span>",
			"22": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>For this reason <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26351AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26351AA\"></sup>Moses has given you circumcision (not because it is from Moses, but from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26351AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26351AB\"></sup>the fathers), and on <i>the</i> Sabbath you circumcise a man.</span>",
			"23": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26352AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26352AC\"></sup>If a man receives circumcision on <i>the</i> Sabbath so that the Law of Moses will not be broken, are you angry with Me because I made an entire man well on <i>the</i> Sabbath?</span>",
			"24": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Do not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26353AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26353AD\"></sup>judge according to appearance, but judge with righteous judgment.”</span>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>So some of the people of Jerusalem were saying, “Is this not the man whom they are seeking to kill?",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Look, He is speaking publicly, and they are saying nothing to Him. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26355AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26355AE\"></sup>The rulers do not really know that this is the Christ, do they?",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>However, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26356AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26356AF\"></sup>we know where this man is from; but whenever the Christ may come, no one knows where He is from.”",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Then Jesus cried out in the temple, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26357AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26357AG\"></sup>teaching and saying, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26357AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26357AH\"></sup>You both know Me and know where I am from; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26357AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26357AI\"></sup>I have not come of Myself, but He who sent Me is true, whom you do not know.</span>",
			"29": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26358AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26358AJ\"></sup>I know Him, because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26358AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26358AK\"></sup>I am from Him, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26358AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26358AL\"></sup>He sent Me.”</span>",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>So they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26359AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26359AM\"></sup>were seeking to seize Him; and no man laid his hand on Him, because His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26359AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26359AN\"></sup>hour had not yet come.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26360AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26360AO\"></sup>many of the crowd believed in Him; and they were saying, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26360AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26360AP\"></sup>When the Christ comes, He will not perform more <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26360AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26360AQ\"></sup>signs than those which this man has, will He?”",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>The Pharisees heard the crowd muttering these things about Him, and the chief priests and the Pharisees sent <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26361AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26361AR\"></sup>officers to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26361AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26361AS\"></sup>seize Him.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>Therefore Jesus said, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26362AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26362AT\"></sup>For a little while longer I am with you, then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26362AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26362AU\"></sup>I go to Him who sent Me.</span>",
			"34": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26363AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26363AV\"></sup>You will seek Me, and will not find Me; and where I am, you cannot come.”</span>",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26364AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26364AW\"></sup>The Jews then said to one another, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26364AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26364AX\"></sup>Where does this man intend to go that we will not find Him? He is not intending to go to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26364AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26364AY\"></sup>the Dispersion among <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26364AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26364AZ\"></sup>the Greeks, and teach the Greeks, is He?",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>What is this statement that He said, <span class=\"woj\">‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26365BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26365BA\"></sup>You will seek Me, and will not find Me; and where I am, you cannot come’</span>?”",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>Now on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26366BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26366BB\"></sup>the last day, the great <i>day</i> of the feast, Jesus stood and cried out, saying, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26366BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26366BC\"></sup>If anyone is thirsty, let him come to Me and drink.</span>",
			"38": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>He who believes in Me, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26367BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26367BD\"></sup>as the Scripture said, ‘From his innermost being will flow rivers of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26367BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26367BE\"></sup>living water.’”</span>",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>But this He spoke <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26368BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26368BF\"></sup>of the Spirit, whom those who believed in Him were to receive; for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26368BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26368BG\"></sup>the Spirit was not yet <i>given</i>, because Jesus was not yet <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26368BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26368BH\"></sup>glorified.",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup><i>Some</i> of the people therefore, when they heard these words, were saying, “This certainly is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26369BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26369BI\"></sup>the Prophet.”",
			"41": "<sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup>Others were saying, “This is the Christ.” Still others were saying, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26370BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26370BJ\"></sup>Surely the Christ is not going to come from Galilee, is He?",
			"42": "<sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup>Has not the Scripture said that the Christ comes from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26371BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26371BK\"></sup>the descendants of David, and from Bethlehem, the village where David was?”",
			"43": "<sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup>So <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26372BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26372BL\"></sup>a division occurred in the crowd because of Him.",
			"44": "<sup class=\"versenum\">44 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26373BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26373BM\"></sup>Some of them wanted to seize Him, but no one laid hands on Him.",
			"45": "<sup class=\"versenum\">45 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26374BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26374BN\"></sup>officers then came to the chief priests and Pharisees, and they said to them, “Why did you not bring Him?”",
			"46": "<sup class=\"versenum\">46 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26375BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26375BO\"></sup>officers answered, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26375BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26375BP\"></sup>Never has a man spoken the way this man speaks.”",
			"47": "<sup class=\"versenum\">47 </sup>The Pharisees then answered them, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26376BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26376BQ\"></sup>You have not also been led astray, have you?",
			"48": "<sup class=\"versenum\">48 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26377BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26377BR\"></sup>No one of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26377BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26377BS\"></sup>the rulers or Pharisees has believed in Him, has he?",
			"49": "<sup class=\"versenum\">49 </sup>But this crowd which does not know the Law is accursed.”",
			"50": "<sup class=\"versenum\">50 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26379BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26379BT\"></sup>Nicodemus (he who came to Him before, being one of them) *said to them,",
			"51": "<sup class=\"versenum\">51 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26380BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26380BU\"></sup>Our Law does not judge a man unless it first hears from him and knows what he is doing, does it?”",
			"52": "<sup class=\"versenum\">52 </sup>They answered him, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26381BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26381BV\"></sup>You are not also from Galilee, are you? Search, and see that no prophet arises out of Galilee.”",
			"53": "<sup class=\"versenum\">53 </sup>[Everyone went to his home."
		},
		"8": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">8 </span>But Jesus went to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26383A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26383A\"></sup>the Mount of Olives.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Early in the morning He came again into the temple, and all the people were coming to Him; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26384B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26384B\"></sup>He sat down and <i>began</i> to teach them.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>The scribes and the Pharisees *brought a woman caught in adultery, and having set her in the center <i>of the court</i>,",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>they *said to Him, “Teacher, this woman has been caught in adultery, in the very act.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Now in the Law <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26387C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26387C\"></sup>Moses commanded us to stone such women; what then do You say?”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>They were saying this, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26388D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26388D\"></sup>testing Him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26388E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26388E\"></sup>so that they might have grounds for accusing Him. But Jesus stooped down and with His finger wrote on the ground.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>But when they persisted in asking Him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26389F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26389F\"></sup>He straightened up, and said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26389G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26389G\"></sup>He who is without sin among you, let him <i>be the</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26389H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26389H\"></sup>first to throw a stone at her.”</span>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Again He stooped down and wrote on the ground.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>When they heard it, they <i>began</i> to go out one by one, beginning with the older ones, and He was left alone, and the woman, where she was, in the center <i>of the court</i>.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26392I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26392I\"></sup>Straightening up, Jesus said to her, <span class=\"woj\">“Woman, where are they? Did no one condemn you?”</span>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>She said, “No one, Lord.” And Jesus said, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26393J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26393J\"></sup>I do not condemn you, either. Go. From now on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26393K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26393K\"></sup>sin no more.”</span>]",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Then Jesus again spoke to them, saying, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26394L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26394L\"></sup>I am the Light of the world; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26394M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26394M\"></sup>he who follows Me will not walk in the darkness, but will have the Light of life.”</span>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>So the Pharisees said to Him, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26395N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26395N\"></sup>You are testifying about Yourself; Your testimony is not true.”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Jesus answered and said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26396O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26396O\"></sup>Even if I testify about Myself, My testimony is true, for I know <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26396P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26396P\"></sup>where I came from and where I am going; but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26396Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26396Q\"></sup>you do not know where I come from or where I am going.</span>",
			"15": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26397R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26397R\"></sup>You judge according to the flesh; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26397S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26397S\"></sup>I am not judging anyone.</span>",
			"16": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>But even <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26398T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26398T\"></sup>if I do judge, My judgment is true; for I am not alone <i>in it</i>, but I and the Father who sent Me.</span>",
			"17": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Even in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26399U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26399U\"></sup>your law it has been written that the testimony of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26399V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26399V\"></sup>two men is true.</span>",
			"18": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>I am He who testifies about Myself, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26400W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26400W\"></sup>the Father who sent Me testifies about Me.”</span>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>So they were saying to Him, “Where is Your Father?” Jesus answered, <span class=\"woj\">“You know neither Me nor My Father; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26401X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26401X\"></sup>if you knew Me, you would know My Father also.”</span>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>These words He spoke in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26402Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26402Y\"></sup>the treasury, as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26402Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26402Z\"></sup>He taught in the temple; and no one seized Him, because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26402AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26402AA\"></sup>His hour had not yet come.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Then He said again to them, <span class=\"woj\">“I go away, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26403AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26403AB\"></sup>you will seek Me, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26403AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26403AC\"></sup>will die in your sin; where I am going, you cannot come.”</span>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>So <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26404AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26404AD\"></sup>the Jews were saying, “Surely He will not kill Himself, will He, since He says, <span class=\"woj\">‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26404AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26404AE\"></sup>Where I am going, you cannot come’</span>?”",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>And He was saying to them, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26405AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26405AF\"></sup>You are from below, I am from above; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26405AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26405AG\"></sup>you are of this world, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26405AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26405AH\"></sup>I am not of this world.</span>",
			"24": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Therefore I said to you that you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26406AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26406AI\"></sup>will die in your sins; for unless you believe that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26406AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26406AJ\"></sup>I am <i>He</i>, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26406AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26406AK\"></sup>you will die in your sins.”</span>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>So they were saying to Him, “Who are You?” Jesus said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“What have I been saying to you <i>from</i> the beginning?</span>",
			"26": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>I have many things to speak and to judge concerning you, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26408AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26408AL\"></sup>He who sent Me is true; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26408AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26408AM\"></sup>the things which I heard from Him, these I speak to the world.”</span>",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>They did not realize that He had been speaking to them about the Father.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>So Jesus said, <span class=\"woj\">“When you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26410AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26410AN\"></sup>lift up the Son of Man, then you will know that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26410AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26410AO\"></sup>I am <i>He</i>, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26410AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26410AP\"></sup>I do nothing on My own initiative, but I speak these things as the Father taught Me.</span>",
			"29": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>And He who sent Me is with Me; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26411AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26411AQ\"></sup>He has not left Me alone, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26411AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26411AR\"></sup>I always do the things that are pleasing to Him.”</span>",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>As He spoke these things, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26412AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26412AS\"></sup>many came to believe in Him.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>So Jesus was saying to those Jews who had believed Him, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26413AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26413AT\"></sup>If you continue in My word, <i>then</i> you are truly <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26413AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26413AU\"></sup>disciples of Mine;</span>",
			"32": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26414AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26414AV\"></sup>you will know the truth, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26414AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26414AW\"></sup>the truth will make you free.”</span>",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>They answered Him, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26415AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26415AX\"></sup>We are Abraham’s descendants and have never yet been enslaved to anyone; how is it that You say, <span class=\"woj\">‘You will become free’?”</span>",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>Jesus answered them, <span class=\"woj\">“Truly, truly, I say to you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26416AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26416AY\"></sup>everyone who commits sin is the slave of sin.</span>",
			"35": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26417AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26417AZ\"></sup>The slave does not remain in the house forever; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26417BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26417BA\"></sup>the son does remain forever.</span>",
			"36": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>So if the Son <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26418BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26418BB\"></sup>makes you free, you will be free indeed.</span>",
			"37": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>I know that you are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26419BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26419BC\"></sup>Abraham’s descendants; yet <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26419BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26419BD\"></sup>you seek to kill Me, because My word has no place in you.</span>",
			"38": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>I speak the things which I have seen with <i>My</i> Father; therefore you also do the things which you heard from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26420BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26420BE\"></sup><i>your</i> father.”</span>",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>They answered and said to Him, “Abraham is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26421BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26421BF\"></sup>our father.” Jesus *said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26421BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26421BG\"></sup>If you are Abraham’s children, do the deeds of Abraham.</span>",
			"40": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>But as it is, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26422BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26422BH\"></sup>you are seeking to kill Me, a man who has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26422BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26422BI\"></sup>told you the truth, which I heard from God; this Abraham did not do.</span>",
			"41": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup>You are doing the deeds of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26423BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26423BJ\"></sup>your father.”</span> They said to Him, “We were not born of fornication; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26423BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26423BK\"></sup>we have one Father: God.”",
			"42": "<sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup>Jesus said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“If God were your Father, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26424BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26424BL\"></sup>you would love Me, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26424BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26424BM\"></sup>for I proceeded forth and have come from God, for I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26424BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26424BN\"></sup>not even come on My own initiative, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26424BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26424BO\"></sup>He sent Me.</span>",
			"43": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup>Why do you not understand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26425BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26425BP\"></sup>what I am saying? <i>It is</i> because you cannot <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26425BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26425BQ\"></sup>hear My word.</span>",
			"44": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">44 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26426BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26426BR\"></sup>You are of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26426BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26426BS\"></sup><i>your</i> father the devil, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26426BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26426BT\"></sup>you want to do the desires of your father. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26426BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26426BU\"></sup>He was a murderer from the beginning, and does not stand in the truth because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26426BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26426BV\"></sup>there is no truth in him. Whenever he speaks a lie, he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26426BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26426BW\"></sup>speaks from his own <i>nature</i>, for he is a liar and the father of lies.</span>",
			"45": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">45 </sup>But because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26427BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26427BX\"></sup>I speak the truth, you do not believe Me.</span>",
			"46": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">46 </sup>Which one of you convicts Me of sin? If <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26428BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26428BY\"></sup>I speak truth, why do you not believe Me?</span>",
			"47": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">47 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26429BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26429BZ\"></sup>He who is of God hears the words of God; for this reason you do not hear <i>them</i>, because you are not of God.”</span>",
			"48": "<sup class=\"versenum\">48 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26430CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26430CA\"></sup>The Jews answered and said to Him, “Do we not say rightly that You are a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26430CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26430CB\"></sup>Samaritan and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26430CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26430CC\"></sup>have a demon?”",
			"49": "<sup class=\"versenum\">49 </sup>Jesus answered, <span class=\"woj\">“I do not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26431CD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CD&quot;&gt;CD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26431CD\"></sup>have a demon; but I honor My Father, and you dishonor Me.</span>",
			"50": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">50 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26432CE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CE&quot;&gt;CE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26432CE\"></sup>I do not seek My glory; there is One who seeks and judges.</span>",
			"51": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">51 </sup>Truly, truly, I say to you, if anyone <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26433CF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CF&quot;&gt;CF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26433CF\"></sup>keeps My word he will never <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26433CG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CG&quot;&gt;CG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26433CG\"></sup>see death.”</span>",
			"52": "<sup class=\"versenum\">52 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26434CH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CH&quot;&gt;CH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26434CH\"></sup>The Jews said to Him, “Now we know that You <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26434CI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CI&quot;&gt;CI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26434CI\"></sup>have a demon. Abraham died, and the prophets <i>also</i>; and You say, <span class=\"woj\">‘If anyone <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26434CJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CJ&quot;&gt;CJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26434CJ\"></sup>keeps My word, he will never <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26434CK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CK&quot;&gt;CK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26434CK\"></sup>taste of death.’</span>",
			"53": "<sup class=\"versenum\">53 </sup>Surely You <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26435CL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CL&quot;&gt;CL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26435CL\"></sup>are not greater than our father Abraham, who died? The prophets died too; whom do You make Yourself out <i>to be</i>?”",
			"54": "<sup class=\"versenum\">54 </sup>Jesus answered, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26436CM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CM&quot;&gt;CM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26436CM\"></sup>If I glorify Myself, My glory is nothing; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26436CN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CN&quot;&gt;CN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26436CN\"></sup>it is My Father who glorifies Me, of whom you say, ‘He is our God’;</span>",
			"55": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">55 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26437CO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CO&quot;&gt;CO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26437CO\"></sup>you have not come to know Him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26437CP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CP&quot;&gt;CP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26437CP\"></sup>but I know Him; and if I say that I do not know Him, I will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26437CQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CQ&quot;&gt;CQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26437CQ\"></sup>a liar like you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26437CR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CR&quot;&gt;CR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26437CR\"></sup>but I do know Him and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26437CS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CS&quot;&gt;CS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26437CS\"></sup>keep His word.</span>",
			"56": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">56 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26438CT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CT&quot;&gt;CT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26438CT\"></sup>Your father Abraham <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26438CU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CU&quot;&gt;CU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26438CU\"></sup>rejoiced to see My day, and he saw <i>it</i> and was glad.”</span>",
			"57": "<sup class=\"versenum\">57 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26439CV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CV&quot;&gt;CV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26439CV\"></sup>So the Jews said to Him, “You are not yet fifty years old, and have You seen Abraham?”",
			"58": "<sup class=\"versenum\">58 </sup>Jesus said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Truly, truly, I say to you, before Abraham was born, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26440CW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CW&quot;&gt;CW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26440CW\"></sup>I am.”</span>",
			"59": "<sup class=\"versenum\">59 </sup>Therefore they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26441CX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CX&quot;&gt;CX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26441CX\"></sup>picked up stones to throw at Him, but Jesus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26441CY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CY&quot;&gt;CY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26441CY\"></sup>hid Himself and went out of the temple."
		},
		"9": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">9 </span>As He passed by, He saw a man blind from birth.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And His disciples asked Him, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26443A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26443A\"></sup>Rabbi, who sinned, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26443B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26443B\"></sup>this man or his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26443C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26443C\"></sup>parents, that he would be born blind?”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Jesus answered, <span class=\"woj\">“<i>It was</i> neither <i>that</i> this man sinned, nor his parents; but <i>it was</i> so <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26444D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26444D\"></sup>that the works of God might be displayed in him.</span>",
			"4": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>We must work the works of Him who sent Me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26445E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26445E\"></sup>as long as it is day; night is coming when no one can work.</span>",
			"5": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>While I am in the world, I am <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26446F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26446F\"></sup>the Light of the world.”</span>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>When He had said this, He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26447G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26447G\"></sup>spat on the ground, and made clay of the spittle, and applied the clay to his eyes,",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>and said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“Go, wash in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26448H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26448H\"></sup>the pool of Siloam”</span> (which is translated, Sent). So he went away and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26448I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26448I\"></sup>washed, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26448J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26448J\"></sup>came <i>back</i> seeing.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Therefore the neighbors, and those who previously saw him as a beggar, were saying, “Is not this the one who used to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26449K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26449K\"></sup>sit and beg?”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Others were saying, “This is he,” <i>still</i> others were saying, “No, but he is like him.” He kept saying, “I am the one.”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>So they were saying to him, “How then were your eyes opened?”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>He answered, “The man who is called Jesus made clay, and anointed my eyes, and said to me, <span class=\"woj\">‘Go to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26452L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26452L\"></sup>Siloam and wash’</span>; so I went away and washed, and I received sight.”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>They said to him, “Where is He?” He *said, “I do not know.”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>They *brought to the Pharisees the man who was formerly blind.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26455M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26455M\"></sup>Now it was a Sabbath on the day when Jesus made the clay and opened his eyes.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26456N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26456N\"></sup>Then the Pharisees also were asking him again how he received his sight. And he said to them, “He applied clay to my eyes, and I washed, and I see.”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Therefore some of the Pharisees were saying, “This man is not from God, because He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26457O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26457O\"></sup>does not keep the Sabbath.” But others were saying, “How can a man who is a sinner perform such <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26457P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26457P\"></sup>signs?” And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26457Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26457Q\"></sup>there was a division among them.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>So they *said to the blind man <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26458R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26458R\"></sup>again, “What do you say about Him, since He opened your eyes?” And he said, “He is a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26458S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26458S\"></sup>prophet.”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26459T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26459T\"></sup>The Jews then did not believe <i>it</i> of him, that he had been blind and had received sight, until they called the parents of the very one who had received his sight,",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>and questioned them, saying, “Is this your son, who you say was born blind? Then how does he now see?”",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>His parents answered them and said, “We know that this is our son, and that he was born blind;",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>but how he now sees, we do not know; or who opened his eyes, we do not know. Ask him; he is of age, he will speak for himself.”",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>His parents said this because they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26463U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26463U\"></sup>were afraid of the Jews; for the Jews <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26463V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26463V\"></sup>had already agreed that if anyone confessed Him to be Christ, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26463W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26463W\"></sup>he was to be put out of the synagogue.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>For this reason his parents said, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26464X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26464X\"></sup>He is of age; ask him.”",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>So a second time they called the man who had been blind, and said to him, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26465Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26465Y\"></sup>Give glory to God; we know that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26465Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26465Z\"></sup>this man is a sinner.”",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>He then answered, “Whether He is a sinner, I do not know; one thing I do know, that though I was blind, now I see.”",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>So they said to him, “What did He do to you? How did He open your eyes?”",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>He answered them, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26468AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26468AA\"></sup>I told you already and you did not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26468AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26468AB\"></sup>listen; why do you want to hear <i>it</i> again? You do not want to become His disciples too, do you?”",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>They reviled him and said, “You are His disciple, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26469AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26469AC\"></sup>we are disciples of Moses.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>We know that God has spoken to Moses, but as for this man, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26470AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26470AD\"></sup>we do not know where He is from.”",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>The man answered and said to them, “Well, here is an amazing thing, that you do not know where He is from, and <i>yet</i> He opened my eyes.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>We know that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26472AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26472AE\"></sup>God does not hear sinners; but if anyone is God-fearing and does His will, He hears him.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>Since the beginning of time it has never been heard that anyone opened the eyes of a person born blind.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26474AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26474AF\"></sup>If this man were not from God, He could do nothing.”",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>They answered him, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26475AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26475AG\"></sup>You were born entirely in sins, and are you teaching us?” So they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26475AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26475AH\"></sup>put him out.",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>Jesus heard that they had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26476AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26476AI\"></sup>put him out, and finding him, He said, <span class=\"woj\">“Do you believe in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26476AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26476AJ\"></sup>Son of Man?”</span>",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>He answered, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26477AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26477AK\"></sup>Who is He, Lord, that I may believe in Him?”",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>Jesus said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“You have both seen Him, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26478AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26478AL\"></sup>He is the one who is talking with you.”</span>",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>And he said, “Lord, I believe.” And he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26479AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26479AM\"></sup>worshiped Him.",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>And Jesus said, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26480AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26480AN\"></sup>For judgment I came into this world, so that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26480AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26480AO\"></sup>those who do not see may see, and that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26480AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26480AP\"></sup>those who see may become blind.”</span>",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>Those of the Pharisees who were with Him heard these things and said to Him, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26481AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26481AQ\"></sup>We are not blind too, are we?”",
			"41": "<sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup>Jesus said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26482AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26482AR\"></sup>If you were blind, you would have no sin; but since you say, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26482AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26482AS\"></sup>We see,’ your sin remains.</span>"
		},
		"10": {
			"1": "<span class=\"woj\"><span class=\"chapternum\">10 </span>“Truly, truly, I say to you, he who does not enter by the door into the fold of the sheep, but climbs up some other way, he is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26483A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26483A\"></sup>a thief and a robber.</span>",
			"2": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>But he who enters by the door is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26484B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26484B\"></sup>a shepherd of the sheep.</span>",
			"3": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>To him the doorkeeper opens, and the sheep hear <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26485C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26485C\"></sup>his voice, and he calls his own sheep by name and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26485D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26485D\"></sup>leads them out.</span>",
			"4": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>When he puts forth all his own, he goes ahead of them, and the sheep follow him because they know <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26486E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26486E\"></sup>his voice.</span>",
			"5": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>A stranger they simply will not follow, but will flee from him, because they do not know <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26487F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26487F\"></sup>the voice of strangers.”</span>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>This <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26488G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26488G\"></sup>figure of speech Jesus spoke to them, but they did not understand what those things were which He had been saying to them.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>So Jesus said to them again, <span class=\"woj\">“Truly, truly, I say to you, I am <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26489H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26489H\"></sup>the door of the sheep.</span>",
			"8": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>All who came before Me are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26490I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26490I\"></sup>thieves and robbers, but the sheep did not hear them.</span>",
			"9": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26491J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26491J\"></sup>I am the door; if anyone enters through Me, he will be saved, and will go in and out and find pasture.</span>",
			"10": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>The thief comes only to steal and kill and destroy; I came that they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26492K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26492K\"></sup>may have life, and have <i>it</i> abundantly.</span>",
			"11": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26493L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26493L\"></sup>I am the good shepherd; the good shepherd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26493M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26493M\"></sup>lays down His life for the sheep.</span>",
			"12": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>He who is a hired hand, and not a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26494N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26494N\"></sup>shepherd, who is not the owner of the sheep, sees the wolf coming, and leaves the sheep and flees, and the wolf snatches them and scatters <i>them</i>.</span>",
			"13": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><i>He flees</i> because he is a hired hand and is not concerned about the sheep.</span>",
			"14": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26496O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26496O\"></sup>I am the good shepherd, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26496P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26496P\"></sup>I know My own and My own know Me,</span>",
			"15": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>even as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26497Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26497Q\"></sup>the Father knows Me and I know the Father; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26497R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26497R\"></sup>I lay down My life for the sheep.</span>",
			"16": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26498S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26498S\"></sup>other sheep, which are not of this fold; I must bring them also, and they will hear My voice; and they will become <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26498T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26498T\"></sup>one flock <i>with</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26498U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26498U\"></sup>one shepherd.</span>",
			"17": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>For this reason the Father loves Me, because I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26499V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26499V\"></sup>lay down My life so that I may take it again.</span>",
			"18": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26500W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26500W\"></sup>No one has taken it away from Me, but I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26500X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26500X\"></sup>lay it down on My own initiative. I have authority to lay it down, and I have authority to take it up again. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26500Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26500Y\"></sup>This commandment I received from My Father.”</span>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26501Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26501Z\"></sup>A division occurred again among the Jews because of these words.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Many of them were saying, “He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26502AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26502AA\"></sup>has a demon and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26502AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26502AB\"></sup>is insane. Why do you listen to Him?”",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Others were saying, “These are not the sayings of one <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26503AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26503AC\"></sup>demon-possessed. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26503AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26503AD\"></sup>A demon cannot open the eyes of the blind, can he?”",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>At that time the Feast of the Dedication took place at Jerusalem;",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>it was winter, and Jesus was walking in the temple in the portico of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26505AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26505AE\"></sup>Solomon.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26506AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26506AF\"></sup>The Jews then gathered around Him, and were saying to Him, “How long will You keep us in suspense? If You are the Christ, tell us <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26506AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26506AG\"></sup>plainly.”",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Jesus answered them, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26507AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26507AH\"></sup>I told you, and you do not believe; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26507AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26507AI\"></sup>the works that I do in My Father’s name, these testify of Me.</span>",
			"26": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>But you do not believe because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26508AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26508AJ\"></sup>you are not of My sheep.</span>",
			"27": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>My sheep <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26509AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26509AK\"></sup>hear My voice, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26509AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26509AL\"></sup>I know them, and they follow Me;</span>",
			"28": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>and I give <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26510AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26510AM\"></sup>eternal life to them, and they will never perish; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26510AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26510AN\"></sup>no one will snatch them out of My hand.</span>",
			"29": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>My Father, who has given <i>them</i> to Me, is greater than all; and no one is able to snatch <i>them</i> out of the Father’s hand.</span>",
			"30": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26512AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26512AO\"></sup>I and the Father are one.”</span>",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>The Jews <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26513AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26513AP\"></sup>picked up stones again to stone Him.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>Jesus answered them, <span class=\"woj\">“I showed you many good works from the Father; for which of them are you stoning Me?”</span>",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>The Jews answered Him, “For a good work we do not stone You, but for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26515AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26515AQ\"></sup>blasphemy; and because You, being a man, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26515AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26515AR\"></sup>make Yourself out <i>to be</i> God.”",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>Jesus answered them, <span class=\"woj\">“Has it not been written in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26516AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26516AS\"></sup>your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26516AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26516AT\"></sup>Law, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26516AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26516AU\"></sup>I <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">said, you are gods</span>’?</span>",
			"35": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>If he called them gods, to whom the word of God came (and the Scripture cannot be broken),</span>",
			"36": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>do you say of Him, whom the Father <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26518AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26518AV\"></sup>sanctified and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26518AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26518AW\"></sup>sent into the world, ‘You are blaspheming,’ because I said, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26518AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26518AX\"></sup>I am the Son of God’?</span>",
			"37": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26519AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26519AY\"></sup>If I do not do the works of My Father, do not believe Me;</span>",
			"38": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>but if I do them, though you do not believe Me, believe <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26520AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26520AZ\"></sup>the works, so that you may know and understand that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26520BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26520BA\"></sup>the Father is in Me, and I in the Father.”</span>",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>Therefore <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26521BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26521BB\"></sup>they were seeking again to seize Him, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26521BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26521BC\"></sup>He eluded their grasp.",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>And He went away <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26522BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26522BD\"></sup>again beyond the Jordan to the place where John was first baptizing, and He was staying there.",
			"41": "<sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup>Many came to Him and were saying, “While John performed no <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26523BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26523BE\"></sup>sign, yet <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26523BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26523BF\"></sup>everything John said about this man was true.”",
			"42": "<sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26524BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26524BG\"></sup>Many believed in Him there."
		},
		"11": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">11 </span>Now a certain man was sick, Lazarus of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26525A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26525A\"></sup>Bethany, the village of Mary and her sister <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26525B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26525B\"></sup>Martha.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>It was the Mary who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26526C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26526C\"></sup>anointed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26526D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26526D\"></sup>the Lord with ointment, and wiped His feet with her hair, whose brother Lazarus was sick.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>So the sisters sent <i>word</i> to Him, saying, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26527E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26527E\"></sup>Lord, behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26527F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26527F\"></sup>he whom You love is sick.”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>But when Jesus heard <i>this</i>, He said, <span class=\"woj\">“This sickness is not to end in death, but for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26528G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26528G\"></sup>the glory of God, so that the Son of God may be glorified by it.”</span>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Now Jesus loved <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26529H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26529H\"></sup>Martha and her sister and Lazarus.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>So when He heard that he was sick, He then stayed two days <i>longer</i> in the place where He was.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Then after this He *said to the disciples, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26531I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26531I\"></sup>Let us go to Judea again.”</span>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The disciples *said to Him, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26532J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26532J\"></sup>Rabbi, the Jews were just now seeking <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26532K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26532K\"></sup>to stone You, and are You going there again?”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Jesus answered, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26533L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26533L\"></sup>Are there not twelve hours in the day? If anyone walks in the day, he does not stumble, because he sees the light of this world.</span>",
			"10": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>But if anyone walks in the night, he stumbles, because the light is not in him.”</span>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>This He said, and after that He *said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Our <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26535M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26535M\"></sup>friend Lazarus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26535N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26535N\"></sup>has fallen asleep; but I go, so that I may awaken him out of sleep.”</span>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>The disciples then said to Him, “Lord, if he has fallen asleep, he will recover.”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26537O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26537O\"></sup>Jesus had spoken of his death, but they thought that He was speaking of literal sleep.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>So Jesus then said to them plainly, <span class=\"woj\">“Lazarus is dead,</span>",
			"15": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>and I am glad for your sakes that I was not there, so that you may believe; but let us go to him.”</span>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26540P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26540P\"></sup>Therefore Thomas, who is called <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26540Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26540Q\"></sup>Didymus, said to <i>his</i> fellow disciples, “Let us also go, so that we may die with Him.”",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>So when Jesus came, He found that he had already been in the tomb <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26541R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26541R\"></sup>four days.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26542S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26542S\"></sup>Bethany was near Jerusalem, about two miles off;",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>and many of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26543T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26543T\"></sup>the Jews had come to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26543U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26543U\"></sup>Martha and Mary, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26543V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26543V\"></sup>to console them concerning <i>their</i> brother.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26544W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26544W\"></sup>Martha therefore, when she heard that Jesus was coming, went to meet Him, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26544X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26544X\"></sup>Mary stayed at the house.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Martha then said to Jesus, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26545Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26545Y\"></sup>Lord, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26545Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26545Z\"></sup>if You had been here, my brother would not have died.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Even now I know that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26546AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26546AA\"></sup>whatever You ask of God, God will give You.”",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Jesus *said to her, <span class=\"woj\">“Your brother will rise again.”</span>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Martha *said to Him, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26548AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26548AB\"></sup>I know that he will rise again in the resurrection on the last day.”",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Jesus said to her, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26549AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26549AC\"></sup>I am the resurrection and the life; he who believes in Me will live even if he dies,</span>",
			"26": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>and everyone who lives and believes in Me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26550AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26550AD\"></sup>will never die. Do you believe this?”</span>",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>She *said to Him, “Yes, Lord; I have believed that You are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26551AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26551AE\"></sup>the Christ, the Son of God, <i>even</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26551AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26551AF\"></sup>He who comes into the world.”",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>When she had said this, she <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26552AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26552AG\"></sup>went away and called Mary her sister, saying secretly, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26552AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26552AH\"></sup>The Teacher is here and is calling for you.”",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>And when she heard it, she *got up quickly and was coming to Him.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>Now Jesus had not yet come into the village, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26554AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26554AI\"></sup>was still in the place where Martha met Him.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26555AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26555AJ\"></sup>Then the Jews who were with her in the house, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26555AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26555AK\"></sup>consoling her, when they saw that Mary got up quickly and went out, they followed her, supposing that she was going to the tomb to weep there.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>Therefore, when Mary came where Jesus was, she saw Him, and fell at His feet, saying to Him, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26556AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26556AL\"></sup>Lord, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26556AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26556AM\"></sup>if You had been here, my brother would not have died.”",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>When Jesus therefore saw her weeping, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26557AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26557AN\"></sup>the Jews who came with her <i>also</i> weeping, He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26557AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26557AO\"></sup>was deeply moved in spirit and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26557AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26557AP\"></sup>was troubled,",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>and said, <span class=\"woj\">“Where have you laid him?”</span> They *said to Him, “Lord, come and see.”",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>Jesus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26559AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26559AQ\"></sup>wept.",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>So <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26560AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26560AR\"></sup>the Jews were saying, “See how He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26560AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26560AS\"></sup>loved him!”",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>But some of them said, “Could not this man, who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26561AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26561AT\"></sup>opened the eyes of the blind man, have kept this man also from dying?”",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>So Jesus, again being deeply moved within, *came to the tomb. Now it was a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26562AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26562AU\"></sup>cave, and a stone was lying against it.",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>Jesus *said, <span class=\"woj\">“Remove the stone.”</span> Martha, the sister of the deceased, *said to Him, “Lord, by this time there will be a stench, for he has been <i>dead</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26563AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26563AV\"></sup>four days.”",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>Jesus *said to her, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26564AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26564AW\"></sup>Did I not say to you that if you believe, you will see the glory of God?”</span>",
			"41": "<sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup>So they removed the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26565AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26565AX\"></sup>stone. Then Jesus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26565AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26565AY\"></sup>raised His eyes, and said, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26565AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26565AZ\"></sup>Father, I thank You that You have heard Me.</span>",
			"42": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup>I knew that You always hear Me; but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26566BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26566BA\"></sup>because of the people standing around I said it, so that they may believe that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26566BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26566BB\"></sup>You sent Me.”</span>",
			"43": "<sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup>When He had said these things, He cried out with a loud voice, <span class=\"woj\">“Lazarus, come forth.”</span>",
			"44": "<sup class=\"versenum\">44 </sup>The man who had died came forth, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26568BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26568BC\"></sup>bound hand and foot with wrappings, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26568BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26568BD\"></sup>his face was wrapped around with a cloth. Jesus *said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Unbind him, and let him go.”</span>",
			"45": "<sup class=\"versenum\">45 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26569BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26569BE\"></sup>Therefore many of the Jews <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26569BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26569BF\"></sup>who came to Mary, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26569BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26569BG\"></sup>saw what He had done, believed in Him.",
			"46": "<sup class=\"versenum\">46 </sup>But some of them went to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26570BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26570BH\"></sup>Pharisees and told them the things which Jesus had done.",
			"47": "<sup class=\"versenum\">47 </sup>Therefore <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26571BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26571BI\"></sup>the chief priests and the Pharisees <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26571BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26571BJ\"></sup>convened a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26571BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26571BK\"></sup>council, and were saying, “What are we doing? For this man is performing many <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26571BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26571BL\"></sup>signs.",
			"48": "<sup class=\"versenum\">48 </sup>If we let Him <i>go on</i> like this, all men will believe in Him, and the Romans will come and take away both our <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26572BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26572BM\"></sup>place and our nation.”",
			"49": "<sup class=\"versenum\">49 </sup>But one of them, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26573BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26573BN\"></sup>Caiaphas, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26573BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26573BO\"></sup>who was high priest that year, said to them, “You know nothing at all,",
			"50": "<sup class=\"versenum\">50 </sup>nor do you take into account that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26574BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26574BP\"></sup>it is expedient for you that one man die for the people, and that the whole nation not perish.”",
			"51": "<sup class=\"versenum\">51 </sup>Now he did not say this on his own initiative, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26575BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26575BQ\"></sup>being high priest that year, he prophesied that Jesus was going to die for the nation,",
			"52": "<sup class=\"versenum\">52 </sup>and not for the nation only, but in order that He might also <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26576BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26576BR\"></sup>gather together into one the children of God who are scattered abroad.",
			"53": "<sup class=\"versenum\">53 </sup>So from that day on they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26577BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26577BS\"></sup>planned together to kill Him.",
			"54": "<sup class=\"versenum\">54 </sup>Therefore Jesus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26578BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26578BT\"></sup>no longer continued to walk publicly among the Jews, but went away from there to the country near the wilderness, into a city called <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26578BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26578BU\"></sup>Ephraim; and there He stayed with the disciples.",
			"55": "<sup class=\"versenum\">55 </sup>Now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26579BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26579BV\"></sup>the Passover of the Jews was near, and many went up to Jerusalem out of the country before the Passover <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26579BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26579BW\"></sup>to purify themselves.",
			"56": "<sup class=\"versenum\">56 </sup>So they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26580BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26580BX\"></sup>were seeking for Jesus, and were saying to one another as they stood in the temple, “What do you think; that He will not come to the feast at all?”",
			"57": "<sup class=\"versenum\">57 </sup>Now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26581BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26581BY\"></sup>the chief priests and the Pharisees had given orders that if anyone knew where He was, he was to report it, so that they might seize Him."
		},
		"12": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">12 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26582A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26582A\"></sup>Jesus, therefore, six days before <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26582B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26582B\"></sup>the Passover, came to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26582C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26582C\"></sup>Bethany where Lazarus was, whom Jesus had raised from the dead.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>So they made Him a supper there, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26583D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26583D\"></sup>Martha was serving; but Lazarus was one of those reclining <i>at the table</i> with Him.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26584E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26584E\"></sup>Mary then took a pound of very costly <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26584F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26584F\"></sup>perfume of pure nard, and anointed the feet of Jesus and wiped His feet with her hair; and the house was filled with the fragrance of the perfume.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26585G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26585G\"></sup>Judas Iscariot, one of His disciples, who was intending to betray Him, *said,",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“Why was this perfume not sold for three hundred denarii and given to poor <i>people</i>?”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Now he said this, not because he was concerned about the poor, but because he was a thief, and as he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26587H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26587H\"></sup>had the money box, he used to pilfer <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26587I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26587I\"></sup>what was put into it.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Therefore Jesus said, <span class=\"woj\">“Let her alone, so that she may keep it for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26588J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26588J\"></sup>the day of My burial.</span>",
			"8": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26589K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26589K\"></sup>For you always have the poor with you, but you do not always have Me.”</span>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26590L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26590L\"></sup>large crowd of the Jews then learned that He was there; and they came, not for Jesus’ sake only, but that they might also see Lazarus, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26590M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26590M\"></sup>whom He raised from the dead.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>But the chief priests planned to put Lazarus to death also;",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26592N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26592N\"></sup>on account of him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26592O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26592O\"></sup>many of the Jews were going away and were believing in Jesus.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>On the next day <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26593P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26593P\"></sup>the large crowd who had come to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26593Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26593Q\"></sup>the feast, when they heard that Jesus was coming to Jerusalem,",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>took the branches of the palm trees and went out to meet Him, and <i>began</i> to shout, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26594R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26594R\"></sup>Hosanna! <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Blessed is He who comes in the name of the Lord</span>, even the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26594S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26594S\"></sup>King of Israel.”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Jesus, finding a young donkey, sat on it; as it is written,",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26596T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26596T\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Fear not, daughter of Zion; behold, your King is coming, seated on a donkey’s colt</span>.”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26597U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26597U\"></sup>These things His disciples did not understand at the first; but when Jesus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26597V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26597V\"></sup>was glorified, then they remembered that these things were written of Him, and that they had done these things to Him.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>So <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26598W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26598W\"></sup>the people, who were with Him when He called Lazarus out of the tomb and raised him from the dead, continued to testify <i>about Him</i>.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26599X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26599X\"></sup>For this reason also the people went and met Him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26599Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26599Y\"></sup>because they heard that He had performed this sign.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>So the Pharisees said to one another, “You see that you are not doing any good; look, the world has gone after Him.”",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Now there were some <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26601Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26601Z\"></sup>Greeks among those who were going up to worship at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26601AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26601AA\"></sup>the feast;",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>these then came to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26602AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26602AB\"></sup>Philip, who was from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26602AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26602AC\"></sup>Bethsaida of Galilee, and <i>began to</i> ask him, saying, “Sir, we wish to see Jesus.”",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Philip *came and *told <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26603AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26603AD\"></sup>Andrew; Andrew and Philip *came and *told Jesus.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>And Jesus *answered them, saying, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26604AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26604AE\"></sup>The hour has come for the Son of Man to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26604AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26604AF\"></sup>be glorified.</span>",
			"24": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Truly, truly, I say to you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26605AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26605AG\"></sup>unless a grain of wheat falls into the earth and dies, it remains alone; but if it dies, it bears much fruit.</span>",
			"25": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26606AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26606AH\"></sup>He who loves his life loses it, and he who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26606AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26606AI\"></sup>hates his life in this world will keep it to life eternal.</span>",
			"26": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>If anyone serves Me, he must follow Me; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26607AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26607AJ\"></sup>where I am, there My servant will be also; if anyone serves Me, the Father will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26607AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26607AK\"></sup>honor him.</span>",
			"27": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26608AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26608AL\"></sup>Now My soul has become troubled; and what shall I say, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26608AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26608AM\"></sup>Father, save Me from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26608AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26608AN\"></sup>this hour’? But for this purpose I came to this hour.</span>",
			"28": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26609AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26609AO\"></sup>Father, glorify Your name.”</span> Then a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26609AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26609AP\"></sup>voice came out of heaven: “I have both glorified it, and will glorify it again.”",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>So the crowd <i>of people</i> who stood by and heard it were saying that it had thundered; others were saying, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26610AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26610AQ\"></sup>An angel has spoken to Him.”",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>Jesus answered and said, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26611AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26611AR\"></sup>This voice has not come for My sake, but for your sakes.</span>",
			"31": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26612AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26612AS\"></sup>Now judgment is upon this world; now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26612AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26612AT\"></sup>the ruler of this world will be cast out.</span>",
			"32": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>And I, if I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26613AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26613AU\"></sup>am lifted up from the earth, will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26613AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26613AV\"></sup>draw all men to Myself.”</span>",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>But He was saying this <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26614AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26614AW\"></sup>to indicate the kind of death by which He was to die.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>The crowd then answered Him, “We have heard out of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26615AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26615AX\"></sup>the Law that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26615AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26615AY\"></sup>the Christ is to remain forever; and how can You say, <span class=\"woj\">‘The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26615AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26615AZ\"></sup>Son of Man must be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26615BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26615BA\"></sup>lifted up’</span>? Who is this <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26615BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26615BB\"></sup>Son of Man?”",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>So Jesus said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26616BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26616BC\"></sup>For a little while longer <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26616BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26616BD\"></sup>the Light is among you. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26616BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26616BE\"></sup>Walk while you have the Light, so that darkness will not overtake you; he who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26616BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26616BF\"></sup>walks in the darkness does not know where he goes.</span>",
			"36": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>While you have the Light, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26617BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26617BG\"></sup>believe in the Light, so that you may become <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26617BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26617BH\"></sup>sons of Light.”</span>These things Jesus spoke, and He went away and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26617BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26617BI\"></sup>hid Himself from them.",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>But though He had performed so many signs before them, <i>yet</i> they were not believing in Him.",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup><i>This was</i> to fulfill the word of Isaiah the prophet which he spoke: “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26619BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26619BJ\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord, who has believed our report</span>? <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">And to whom has the arm of the Lord been revealed</span>?”",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>For this reason they could not believe, for Isaiah said again,",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26621BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26621BK\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">He has blinded their eyes and He</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26621BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26621BL\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">hardened their heart, so that they would not see with their eyes and perceive with their heart, and</span> <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">be converted and I heal them</span>.”",
			"41": "<sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup>These things Isaiah said because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26622BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26622BM\"></sup>he saw His glory, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26622BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26622BN\"></sup>he spoke of Him.",
			"42": "<sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup>Nevertheless <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26623BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26623BO\"></sup>many even of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26623BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26623BP\"></sup>the rulers believed in Him, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26623BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26623BQ\"></sup>because of the Pharisees they were not confessing <i>Him</i>, for fear that they would be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26623BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26623BR\"></sup>put out of the synagogue;",
			"43": "<sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26624BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26624BS\"></sup>for they loved the approval of men rather than the approval of God.",
			"44": "<sup class=\"versenum\">44 </sup>And Jesus cried out and said, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26625BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26625BT\"></sup>He who believes in Me, does not believe in Me but in Him who sent Me.</span>",
			"45": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">45 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26626BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26626BU\"></sup>He who sees Me sees the One who sent Me.</span>",
			"46": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">46 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26627BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26627BV\"></sup>I have come <i>as</i> Light into the world, so that everyone who believes in Me will not remain in darkness.</span>",
			"47": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">47 </sup>If anyone hears My sayings and does not keep them, I do not judge him; for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26628BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26628BW\"></sup>I did not come to judge the world, but to save the world.</span>",
			"48": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">48 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26629BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26629BX\"></sup>He who rejects Me and does not receive My sayings, has one who judges him; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26629BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26629BY\"></sup>the word I spoke is what will judge him at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26629BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26629BZ\"></sup>the last day.</span>",
			"49": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">49 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26630CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26630CA\"></sup>For I did not speak on My own initiative, but the Father Himself who sent Me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26630CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26630CB\"></sup>has given Me a commandment <i>as to</i> what to say and what to speak.</span>",
			"50": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">50 </sup>I know that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26631CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26631CC\"></sup>His commandment is eternal life; therefore the things I speak, I speak <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26631CD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CD&quot;&gt;CD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26631CD\"></sup>just as the Father has told Me.”</span>"
		},
		"13": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">13 </span>Now before the Feast of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26632A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26632A\"></sup>the Passover, Jesus knowing that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26632B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26632B\"></sup>His hour had come that He would depart out of this world <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26632C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26632C\"></sup>to the Father, having loved His own who were in the world, He loved them to the end.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>During supper, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26633D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26633D\"></sup>the devil having already put into the heart of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26633E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26633E\"></sup>Judas Iscariot, <i>the son</i> of Simon, to betray Him,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><i>Jesus</i>, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26634F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26634F\"></sup>knowing that the Father had given all things into His hands, and that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26634G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26634G\"></sup>He had come forth from God and was going back to God,",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>*got up from supper, and *laid aside His garments; and taking a towel, He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26635H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26635H\"></sup>girded Himself.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Then He *poured water into the basin, and began to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26636I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26636I\"></sup>wash the disciples’ feet and to wipe them with the towel with which He was girded.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>So He *came to Simon Peter. He *said to Him, “Lord, do You wash my feet?”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Jesus answered and said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“What I do you do not realize now, but you will understand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26638J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26638J\"></sup>hereafter.”</span>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Peter *said to Him, “Never shall You wash my feet!” Jesus answered him, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26639K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26639K\"></sup>If I do not wash you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26639L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26639L\"></sup>you have no part with Me.”</span>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Simon Peter *said to Him, “Lord, <i>then wash</i> not only my feet, but also my hands and my head.”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Jesus *said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“He who has bathed needs only to wash his feet, but is completely clean; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26641M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26641M\"></sup>you are clean, but not all <i>of you</i>.”</span>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26642N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26642N\"></sup>He knew the one who was betraying Him; for this reason He said, <span class=\"woj\">“Not all of you are clean.”</span>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>So when He had washed their feet, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26643O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26643O\"></sup>taken His garments and reclined <i>at the table</i> again, He said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Do you know what I have done to you?</span>",
			"13": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>You call Me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26644P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26644P\"></sup>Teacher and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26644Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26644Q\"></sup>Lord; and you are right, for <i>so</i> I am.</span>",
			"14": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>If I then, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26645R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26645R\"></sup>the Lord and the Teacher, washed your feet, you also ought to wash one another’s feet.</span>",
			"15": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>For I gave you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26646S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26646S\"></sup>an example that you also should do as I did to you.</span>",
			"16": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Truly, truly, I say to you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26647T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26647T\"></sup>a slave is not greater than his master, nor <i>is</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26647U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26647U\"></sup>one who is sent greater than the one who sent him.</span>",
			"17": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>If you know these things, you are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26648V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26648V\"></sup>blessed if you do them.</span>",
			"18": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26649W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26649W\"></sup>I do not speak of all of you. I know the ones I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26649X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26649X\"></sup>chosen; but <i>it is</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26649Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26649Y\"></sup>that the Scripture may be fulfilled, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26649Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26649Z\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">He who eats My bread has lifted up his heel against Me</span>.’</span>",
			"19": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>From now on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26650AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26650AA\"></sup>I am telling you before <i>it</i> comes to pass, so that when it does occur, you may believe that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26650AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26650AB\"></sup>I am <i>He</i>.</span>",
			"20": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Truly, truly, I say to you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26651AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26651AC\"></sup>he who receives whomever I send receives Me; and he who receives Me receives Him who sent Me.”</span>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>When Jesus had said this, He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26652AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26652AD\"></sup>became troubled in spirit, and testified and said, <span class=\"woj\">“Truly, truly, I say to you, that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26652AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26652AE\"></sup>one of you will betray Me.”</span>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>The disciples <i>began</i> looking at one another, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26653AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26653AF\"></sup>at a loss <i>to know</i> of which one He was speaking.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>There was reclining on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26654AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26654AG\"></sup>Jesus’ bosom one of His disciples, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26654AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26654AH\"></sup>whom Jesus loved.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>So Simon Peter *gestured to him, and *said to him, “Tell <i>us</i> who it is of whom He is speaking.”",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>He, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26656AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26656AI\"></sup>leaning back thus on Jesus’ bosom, *said to Him, “Lord, who is it?”",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Jesus then *answered, <span class=\"woj\">“That is the one for whom I shall dip the morsel and give it to him.”</span> So when He had dipped the morsel, He *took and *gave it to Judas, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26657AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26657AJ\"></sup><i>the son</i> of Simon Iscariot.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>After the morsel, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26658AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26658AK\"></sup>Satan then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26658AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26658AL\"></sup>entered into him. Therefore Jesus *said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“What you do, do quickly.”</span>",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Now no one of those reclining <i>at the table</i> knew for what purpose He had said this to him.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>For some were supposing, because Judas <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26660AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26660AM\"></sup>had the money box, that Jesus was saying to him, “Buy the things we have need of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26660AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26660AN\"></sup>for the feast”; or else, that he should <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26660AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26660AO\"></sup>give something to the poor.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>So after receiving the morsel he went out immediately; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26661AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26661AP\"></sup>it was night.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>Therefore when he had gone out, Jesus *said, <span class=\"woj\">“Now is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26662AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26662AQ\"></sup>the Son of Man <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26662AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26662AR\"></sup>glorified, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26662AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26662AS\"></sup>God is glorified in Him;</span>",
			"32": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>if God is glorified in Him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26663AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26663AT\"></sup>God will also glorify Him in Himself, and will glorify Him immediately.</span>",
			"33": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26664AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26664AU\"></sup>Little children, I am with you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26664AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26664AV\"></sup>a little while longer. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26664AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26664AW\"></sup>You will seek Me; and as I said to the Jews, now I also say to you, ‘Where I am going, you cannot come.’</span>",
			"34": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>A <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26665AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26665AX\"></sup>new commandment I give to you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26665AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26665AY\"></sup>that you love one another, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26665AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26665AZ\"></sup>even as I have loved you, that you also love one another.</span>",
			"35": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26666BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26666BA\"></sup>By this all men will know that you are My disciples, if you have love for one another.”</span>",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>Simon Peter *said to Him, “Lord, where are You going?” Jesus answered, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26667BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26667BB\"></sup>Where I go, you cannot follow Me now; but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26667BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26667BC\"></sup>you will follow later.”</span>",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>Peter *said to Him, “Lord, why can I not follow You right now? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26668BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26668BD\"></sup>I will lay down my life for You.”",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>Jesus *answered, <span class=\"woj\">“Will you lay down your life for Me? Truly, truly, I say to you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26669BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26669BE\"></sup>a rooster will not crow until you deny Me three times.</span>"
		},
		"14": {
			"1": "<span class=\"woj\"><span class=\"chapternum\">14 </span>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26670A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26670A\"></sup>Do not let your heart be troubled; believe in God, believe also in Me.</span>",
			"2": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>In My Father’s house are many dwelling places; if it were not so, I would have told you; for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26671B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26671B\"></sup>I go to prepare a place for you.</span>",
			"3": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>If I go and prepare a place for you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26672C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26672C\"></sup>I will come again and receive you to Myself, that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26672D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26672D\"></sup>where I am, <i>there</i> you may be also.</span>",
			"4": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>And you know the way where I am going.”</span>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26674E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26674E\"></sup>Thomas *said to Him, “Lord, we do not know where You are going, how do we know the way?”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Jesus *said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“I am <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26675F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26675F\"></sup>the way, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26675G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26675G\"></sup>the truth, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26675H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26675H\"></sup>the life; no one comes to the Father but through Me.</span>",
			"7": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26676I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26676I\"></sup>If you had known Me, you would have known My Father also; from now on you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26676J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26676J\"></sup>know Him, and have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26676K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26676K\"></sup>seen Him.”</span>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26677L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26677L\"></sup>Philip *said to Him, “Lord, show us the Father, and it is enough for us.”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Jesus *said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“Have I been so long with you, and <i>yet</i> you have not come to know Me, Philip? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26678M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26678M\"></sup>He who has seen Me has seen the Father; how <i>can</i> you say, ‘Show us the Father’?</span>",
			"10": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Do you not believe that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26679N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26679N\"></sup>I am in the Father, and the Father is in Me? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26679O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26679O\"></sup>The words that I say to you I do not speak on My own initiative, but the Father abiding in Me does His works.</span>",
			"11": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Believe Me that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26680P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26680P\"></sup>I am in the Father and the Father is in Me; otherwise <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26680Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26680Q\"></sup>believe because of the works themselves.</span>",
			"12": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Truly, truly, I say to you, he who believes in Me, the works that I do, he will do also; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26681R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26681R\"></sup>greater <i>works</i> than these he will do; because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26681S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26681S\"></sup>I go to the Father.</span>",
			"13": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26682T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26682T\"></sup>Whatever you ask in My name, that will I do, so that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26682U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26682U\"></sup>the Father may be glorified in the Son.</span>",
			"14": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>If you ask Me anything <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26683V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26683V\"></sup>in My name, I will do <i>it</i>.</span>",
			"15": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26684W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26684W\"></sup>If you love Me, you will keep My commandments.</span>",
			"16": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>I will ask the Father, and He will give you another <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26685X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26685X\"></sup>Helper, that He may be with you forever;</span>",
			"17": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><i>that is</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26686Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26686Y\"></sup>the Spirit of truth, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26686Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26686Z\"></sup>whom the world cannot receive, because it does not see Him or know Him, <i>but</i> you know Him because He abides with you and will be in you.</span>",
			"18": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“I will not leave you as orphans; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26687AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26687AA\"></sup>I will come to you.</span>",
			"19": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26688AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26688AB\"></sup>After a little while <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26688AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26688AC\"></sup>the world will no longer see Me, but you <i>will</i> see Me; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26688AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26688AD\"></sup>because I live, you will live also.</span>",
			"20": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26689AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26689AE\"></sup>In that day you will know that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26689AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26689AF\"></sup>I am in My Father, and you in Me, and I in you.</span>",
			"21": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26690AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26690AG\"></sup>He who has My commandments and keeps them is the one who loves Me; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26690AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26690AH\"></sup>he who loves Me will be loved by My Father, and I will love him and will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26690AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26690AI\"></sup>disclose Myself to him.”</span>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26691AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26691AJ\"></sup>Judas (not Iscariot) *said to Him, “Lord, what then has happened <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26691AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26691AK\"></sup>that You are going to disclose Yourself to us and not to the world?”",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Jesus answered and said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26692AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26692AL\"></sup>If anyone loves Me, he will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26692AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26692AM\"></sup>keep My word; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26692AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26692AN\"></sup>My Father will love him, and We <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26692AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26692AO\"></sup>will come to him and make Our abode with him.</span>",
			"24": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>He who does not love Me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26693AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26693AP\"></sup>does not keep My words; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26693AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26693AQ\"></sup>the word which you hear is not Mine, but the Father’s who sent Me.</span>",
			"25": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>“These things I have spoken to you while abiding with you.</span>",
			"26": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>But the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26695AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26695AR\"></sup>Helper, the Holy Spirit, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26695AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26695AS\"></sup>whom the Father will send in My name, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26695AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26695AT\"></sup>He will teach you all things, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26695AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26695AU\"></sup>bring to your remembrance all that I said to you.</span>",
			"27": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26696AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26696AV\"></sup>Peace I leave with you; My peace I give to you; not as the world gives do I give to you. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26696AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26696AW\"></sup>Do not let your heart be troubled, nor let it be fearful.</span>",
			"28": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26697AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26697AX\"></sup>You heard that I said to you, ‘I go away, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26697AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26697AY\"></sup>I will come to you.’ If you loved Me, you would have rejoiced because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26697AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26697AZ\"></sup>I go to the Father, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26697BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26697BA\"></sup>the Father is greater than I.</span>",
			"29": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>Now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26698BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26698BB\"></sup>I have told you before it happens, so that when it happens, you may believe.</span>",
			"30": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>I will not speak much more with you, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26699BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26699BC\"></sup>the ruler of the world is coming, and he has nothing in Me;</span>",
			"31": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>but so that the world may know that I love the Father, I do exactly as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26700BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26700BD\"></sup>the Father commanded Me. Get up, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26700BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26700BE\"></sup>let us go from here.</span>"
		},
		"15": {
			"1": "<span class=\"woj\"><span class=\"chapternum\">15 </span>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26701A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26701A\"></sup>I am the true vine, and My Father is the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26701B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26701B\"></sup>vinedresser.</span>",
			"2": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Every branch in Me that does not bear fruit, He takes away; and every <i>branch</i> that bears fruit, He prunes it so that it may bear more fruit.</span>",
			"3": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26703C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26703C\"></sup>You are already clean because of the word which I have spoken to you.</span>",
			"4": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26704D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26704D\"></sup>Abide in Me, and I in you. As the branch cannot bear fruit of itself unless it abides in the vine, so neither <i>can</i> you unless you abide in Me.</span>",
			"5": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>I am the vine, you are the branches; he who abides in Me and I in him, he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26705E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26705E\"></sup>bears much fruit, for apart from Me you can do nothing.</span>",
			"6": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>If anyone does not abide in Me, he is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26706F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26706F\"></sup>thrown away as a branch and dries up; and they gather them, and cast them into the fire and they are burned.</span>",
			"7": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>If you abide in Me, and My words abide in you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26707G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26707G\"></sup>ask whatever you wish, and it will be done for you.</span>",
			"8": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26708H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26708H\"></sup>Father is glorified by this, that you bear much fruit, and <i>so</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26708I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26708I\"></sup>prove to be My disciples.</span>",
			"9": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Just as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26709J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26709J\"></sup>the Father has loved Me, I have also loved you; abide in My love.</span>",
			"10": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26710K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26710K\"></sup>If you keep My commandments, you will abide in My love; just as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26710L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26710L\"></sup>I have kept My Father’s commandments and abide in His love.</span>",
			"11": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26711M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26711M\"></sup>These things I have spoken to you so that My joy may be in you, and <i>that</i> your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26711N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26711N\"></sup>joy may be made full.</span>",
			"12": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“This is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26712O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26712O\"></sup>My commandment, that you love one another, just as I have loved you.</span>",
			"13": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26713P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26713P\"></sup>Greater love has no one than this, that one <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26713Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26713Q\"></sup>lay down his life for his friends.</span>",
			"14": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>You are My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26714R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26714R\"></sup>friends if <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26714S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26714S\"></sup>you do what I command you.</span>",
			"15": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>No longer do I call you slaves, for the slave does not know what his master is doing; but I have called you friends, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26715T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26715T\"></sup>all things that I have heard from My Father I have made known to you.</span>",
			"16": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26716U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26716U\"></sup>You did not choose Me but I chose you, and appointed you that you would go and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26716V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26716V\"></sup>bear fruit, and <i>that</i> your fruit would remain, so that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26716W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26716W\"></sup>whatever you ask of the Father in My name He may give to you.</span>",
			"17": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>This <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26717X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26717X\"></sup>I command you, that you love one another.</span>",
			"18": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26718Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26718Y\"></sup>If the world hates you, you know that it has hated Me before <i>it hated</i> you.</span>",
			"19": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>If you were of the world, the world would love its own; but because you are not of the world, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26719Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26719Z\"></sup>I chose you out of the world, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26719AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26719AA\"></sup>because of this the world hates you.</span>",
			"20": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Remember the word that I said to you, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26720AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26720AB\"></sup>A slave is not greater than his master.’ If they persecuted Me, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26720AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26720AC\"></sup>they will also persecute you; if they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26720AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26720AD\"></sup>kept My word, they will keep yours also.</span>",
			"21": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>But all these things they will do to you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26721AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26721AE\"></sup>for My name’s sake, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26721AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26721AF\"></sup>because they do not know the One who sent Me.</span>",
			"22": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26722AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26722AG\"></sup>If I had not come and spoken to them, they would not have sin, but now they have no excuse for their sin.</span>",
			"23": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>He who hates Me hates My Father also.</span>",
			"24": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26724AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26724AH\"></sup>If I had not done among them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26724AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26724AI\"></sup>the works which no one else did, they would not have sin; but now they have both seen and hated Me and My Father as well.</span>",
			"25": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>But <i>they have done this</i> to fulfill the word that is written in their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26725AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26725AJ\"></sup>Law, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26725AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26725AK\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">They hated Me without a cause</span>.’</span>",
			"26": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>“When the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26726AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26726AL\"></sup>Helper comes, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26726AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26726AM\"></sup>whom I will send to you from the Father, <i>that is</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26726AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26726AN\"></sup>the Spirit of truth who proceeds from the Father, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26726AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26726AO\"></sup>He will testify about Me,</span>",
			"27": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26727AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26727AP\"></sup>you <i>will</i> testify also, because you have been with Me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26727AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26727AQ\"></sup>from the beginning.</span>"
		},
		"16": {
			"1": "<span class=\"woj\"><span class=\"chapternum\">16 </span>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26728A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26728A\"></sup>These things I have spoken to you so that you may be kept from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26728B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26728B\"></sup>stumbling.</span>",
			"2": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>They will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26729C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26729C\"></sup>make you outcasts from the synagogue, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26729D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26729D\"></sup>an hour is coming for everyone <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26729E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26729E\"></sup>who kills you to think that he is offering service to God.</span>",
			"3": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>These things they will do <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26730F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26730F\"></sup>because they have not known the Father or Me.</span>",
			"4": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>But these things I have spoken to you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26731G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26731G\"></sup>so that when their hour comes, you may remember that I told you of them. These things I did not say to you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26731H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26731H\"></sup>at the beginning, because I was with you.</span>",
			"5": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“But now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26732I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26732I\"></sup>I am going to Him who sent Me; and none of you asks Me, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26732J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26732J\"></sup>Where are You going?’</span>",
			"6": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>But because I have said these things to you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26733K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26733K\"></sup>sorrow has filled your heart.</span>",
			"7": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>But I tell you the truth, it is to your advantage that I go away; for if I do not go away, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26734L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26734L\"></sup>Helper will not come to you; but if I go, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26734M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26734M\"></sup>I will send Him to you.</span>",
			"8": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>And He, when He comes, will convict the world concerning sin and righteousness and judgment;</span>",
			"9": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>concerning sin, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26736N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26736N\"></sup>because they do not believe in Me;</span>",
			"10": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>and concerning <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26737O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26737O\"></sup>righteousness, because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26737P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26737P\"></sup>I go to the Father and you no longer see Me;</span>",
			"11": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26738Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26738Q\"></sup>and concerning judgment, because the ruler of this world has been judged.</span>",
			"12": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“I have many more things to say to you, but you cannot bear <i>them</i> now.</span>",
			"13": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>But when He, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26740R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26740R\"></sup>the Spirit of truth, comes, He will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26740S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26740S\"></sup>guide you into all the truth; for He will not speak on His own initiative, but whatever He hears, He will speak; and He will disclose to you what is to come.</span>",
			"14": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>He will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26741T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26741T\"></sup>glorify Me, for He will take of Mine and will disclose <i>it</i> to you.</span>",
			"15": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26742U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26742U\"></sup>All things that the Father has are Mine; therefore I said that He takes of Mine and will disclose <i>it</i> to you.</span>",
			"16": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26743V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26743V\"></sup>A little while, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26743W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26743W\"></sup>you will no longer see Me; and again a little while, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26743X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26743X\"></sup>you will see Me.”</span>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><i>Some</i> of His disciples then said to one another, “What is this thing He is telling us, <span class=\"woj\">‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26744Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26744Y\"></sup>A little while, and you will not see Me; and again a little while, and you will see Me’</span>; and, <span class=\"woj\">‘because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26744Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26744Z\"></sup>I go to the Father’</span>?”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>So they were saying, “What is this that He says, <span class=\"woj\">‘A little while’</span>? We do not know what He is talking about.”",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26746AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26746AA\"></sup>Jesus knew that they wished to question Him, and He said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Are you deliberating together about this, that I said, ‘A little while, and you will not see Me, and again a little while, and you will see Me’?</span>",
			"20": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Truly, truly, I say to you, that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26747AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26747AB\"></sup>you will weep and lament, but the world will rejoice; you will grieve, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26747AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26747AC\"></sup>your grief will be turned into joy.</span>",
			"21": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26748AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26748AD\"></sup>Whenever a woman is in labor she has pain, because her hour has come; but when she gives birth to the child, she no longer remembers the anguish because of the joy that a child has been born into the world.</span>",
			"22": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Therefore <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26749AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26749AE\"></sup>you too have grief now; but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26749AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26749AF\"></sup>I will see you again, and your heart will rejoice, and no one <i>will</i> take your joy away from you.</span>",
			"23": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26750AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26750AG\"></sup>In that day <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26750AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26750AH\"></sup>you will not question Me about anything. Truly, truly, I say to you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26750AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26750AI\"></sup>if you ask the Father for anything in My name, He will give it to you.</span>",
			"24": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26751AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26751AJ\"></sup>Until now you have asked for nothing in My name; ask and you will receive, so that your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26751AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26751AK\"></sup>joy may be made full.</span>",
			"25": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>“These things I have spoken to you in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26752AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26752AL\"></sup>figurative language; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26752AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26752AM\"></sup>an hour is coming when I will no longer speak to you in figurative language, but will tell you plainly of the Father.</span>",
			"26": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26753AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26753AN\"></sup>In that day <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26753AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26753AO\"></sup>you will ask in My name, and I do not say to you that I will request of the Father on your behalf;</span>",
			"27": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26754AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26754AP\"></sup>the Father Himself loves you, because you have loved Me and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26754AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26754AQ\"></sup>have believed that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26754AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26754AR\"></sup>I came forth from the Father.</span>",
			"28": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26755AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26755AS\"></sup>I came forth from the Father and have come into the world; I am leaving the world again and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26755AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26755AT\"></sup>going to the Father.”</span>",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>His disciples *said, “Lo, now You are speaking plainly and are not using <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26756AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26756AU\"></sup>a figure of speech.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>Now we know that You know all things, and have no need for anyone to question You; by this we <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26757AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26757AV\"></sup>believe that You <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26757AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26757AW\"></sup>came from God.”",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>Jesus answered them, <span class=\"woj\">“Do you now believe?</span>",
			"32": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>Behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26759AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26759AX\"></sup>an hour is coming, and has <i>already</i> come, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26759AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26759AY\"></sup>you to be scattered, each to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26759AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26759AZ\"></sup>his own <i>home</i>, and to leave Me alone; and <i>yet</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26759BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26759BA\"></sup>I am not alone, because the Father is with Me.</span>",
			"33": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>These things I have spoken to you, so that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26760BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26760BB\"></sup>in Me you may have peace. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26760BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26760BC\"></sup>In the world you have tribulation, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26760BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26760BD\"></sup>take courage; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26760BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26760BE\"></sup>I have overcome the world.”</span>"
		},
		"17": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">17 </span>Jesus spoke these things; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26761A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26761A\"></sup>lifting up His eyes to heaven, He said, <span class=\"woj\">“Father, the hour has come; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26761B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26761B\"></sup>glorify Your Son, that the Son may glorify You,</span>",
			"2": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>even as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26762C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26762C\"></sup>You gave Him authority over all flesh, that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26762D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26762D\"></sup>to all whom You have given Him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26762E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26762E\"></sup>He may give eternal life.</span>",
			"3": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>This is eternal life, that they may know You, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26763F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26763F\"></sup>the only true God, and Jesus Christ whom <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26763G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26763G\"></sup>You have sent.</span>",
			"4": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26764H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26764H\"></sup>I glorified You on the earth, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26764I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26764I\"></sup>having accomplished the work which You have given Me to do.</span>",
			"5": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Now, Father, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26765J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26765J\"></sup>glorify Me together with Yourself, with the glory which I had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26765K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26765K\"></sup>with You before the world was.</span>",
			"6": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26766L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26766L\"></sup>I have manifested Your name to the men whom <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26766M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26766M\"></sup>You gave Me out of the world; they were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26766N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26766N\"></sup>Yours and You gave them to Me, and they have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26766O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26766O\"></sup>kept Your word.</span>",
			"7": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Now they have come to know that everything You have given Me is from You;</span>",
			"8": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26768P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26768P\"></sup>the words which You gave Me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26768Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26768Q\"></sup>I have given to them; and they received <i>them</i> and truly understood that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26768R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26768R\"></sup>I came forth from You, and they believed that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26768S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26768S\"></sup>You sent Me.</span>",
			"9": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26769T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26769T\"></sup>I ask on their behalf; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26769U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26769U\"></sup>I do not ask on behalf of the world, but of those whom <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26769V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26769V\"></sup>You have given Me; for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26769W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26769W\"></sup>they are Yours;</span>",
			"10": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26770X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26770X\"></sup>all things that are Mine are Yours, and Yours are Mine; and I have been glorified in them.</span>",
			"11": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>I am no longer in the world; and <i>yet</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26771Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26771Y\"></sup>they themselves are in the world, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26771Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26771Z\"></sup>I come to You. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26771AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26771AA\"></sup>Holy Father, keep them in Your name, <i>the name</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26771AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26771AB\"></sup>which You have given Me, that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26771AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26771AC\"></sup>they may be one even as We <i>are</i>.</span>",
			"12": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>While I was with them, I was keeping them in Your name <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26772AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26772AD\"></sup>which You have given Me; and I guarded them and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26772AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26772AE\"></sup>not one of them perished but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26772AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26772AF\"></sup>the son of perdition, so that the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26772AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26772AG\"></sup>Scripture would be fulfilled.</span>",
			"13": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>But now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26773AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26773AH\"></sup>I come to You; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26773AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26773AI\"></sup>these things I speak in the world so that they may have My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26773AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26773AJ\"></sup>joy made full in themselves.</span>",
			"14": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>I have given them Your word; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26774AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26774AK\"></sup>the world has hated them, because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26774AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26774AL\"></sup>they are not of the world, even as I am not of the world.</span>",
			"15": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>I do not ask You to take them out of the world, but to keep them from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26775AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26775AM\"></sup>the evil <i>one</i>.</span>",
			"16": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26776AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26776AN\"></sup>They are not of the world, even as I am not of the world.</span>",
			"17": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26777AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26777AO\"></sup>Sanctify them in the truth; Your word is truth.</span>",
			"18": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>As <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26778AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26778AP\"></sup>You sent Me into the world, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26778AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26778AQ\"></sup>I also have sent them into the world.</span>",
			"19": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>For their sakes I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26779AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26779AR\"></sup>sanctify Myself, that they themselves also may be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26779AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26779AS\"></sup>sanctified <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26779AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26779AT\"></sup>in truth.</span>",
			"20": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“I do not ask on behalf of these alone, but for those also who believe in Me through their word;</span>",
			"21": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>that they may all be one; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26781AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26781AU\"></sup>even as You, Father, <i>are</i> in Me and I in You, that they also may be in Us, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26781AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26781AV\"></sup>so that the world may believe that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26781AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26781AW\"></sup>You sent Me.</span>",
			"22": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26782AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26782AX\"></sup>glory which You have given Me I have given to them, that they may be one, just as We are one;</span>",
			"23": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26783AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26783AY\"></sup>I in them and You in Me, that they may be perfected in unity, so that the world may know that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26783AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26783AZ\"></sup>You sent Me, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26783BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26783BA\"></sup>loved them, even as You have loved Me.</span>",
			"24": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Father, I desire that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26784BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26784BB\"></sup>they also, whom You have given Me, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26784BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26784BC\"></sup>be with Me where I am, so that they may see My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26784BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26784BD\"></sup>glory which You have given Me, for You loved Me before <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26784BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26784BE\"></sup>the foundation of the world.</span>",
			"25": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>“O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26785BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26785BF\"></sup>righteous Father, although <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26785BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26785BG\"></sup>the world has not known You, yet I have known You; and these have known that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26785BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26785BH\"></sup>You sent Me;</span>",
			"26": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26786BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26786BI\"></sup>I have made Your name known to them, and will make it known, so that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26786BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26786BJ\"></sup>the love with which You loved Me may be in them, and I in them.”</span>"
		},
		"18": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">18 </span>When Jesus had spoken these words, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26787A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26787A\"></sup>He went forth with His disciples over <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26787B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26787B\"></sup>the ravine of the Kidron, where there was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26787C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26787C\"></sup>a garden, in which He entered with His disciples.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Now Judas also, who was betraying Him, knew the place, for Jesus had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26788D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26788D\"></sup>often met there with His disciples.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26789E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26789E\"></sup>Judas then, having received <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26789F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26789F\"></sup>the <i>Roman</i> cohort and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26789G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26789G\"></sup>officers from the chief priests and the Pharisees, *came there with lanterns and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26789H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26789H\"></sup>torches and weapons.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>So Jesus, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26790I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26790I\"></sup>knowing all the things that were coming upon Him, went forth and *said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26790J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26790J\"></sup>Whom do you seek?”</span>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>They answered Him, “Jesus the Nazarene.” He *said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“I am <i>He</i>.”</span> And Judas also, who was betraying Him, was standing with them.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>So when He said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“I am <i>He</i>,”</span> they drew back and fell to the ground.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Therefore He again asked them, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26793K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26793K\"></sup>Whom do you seek?”</span> And they said, “Jesus the Nazarene.”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Jesus answered, <span class=\"woj\">“I told you that I am <i>He</i>; so if you seek Me, let these go their way,”</span>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>to fulfill the word which He spoke, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26795L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26795L\"></sup>Of those whom You have given Me I lost not one.”</span>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Simon Peter then, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26796M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26796M\"></sup>having a sword, drew it and struck the high priest’s slave, and cut off his right ear; and the slave’s name was Malchus.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>So Jesus said to Peter, <span class=\"woj\">“Put the sword into the sheath; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26797N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26797N\"></sup>the cup which the Father has given Me, shall I not drink it?”</span>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26798O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26798O\"></sup>So <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26798P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26798P\"></sup>the <i>Roman</i> cohort and the commander and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26798Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26798Q\"></sup>officers of the Jews, arrested Jesus and bound Him,",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>and led Him to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26799R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26799R\"></sup>Annas first; for he was father-in-law of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26799S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26799S\"></sup>Caiaphas, who was high priest that year.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Now Caiaphas was the one who had advised the Jews that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26800T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26800T\"></sup>it was expedient for one man to die on behalf of the people.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26801U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26801U\"></sup>Simon Peter was following Jesus, and <i>so was</i> another disciple. Now that disciple was known to the high priest, and entered with Jesus into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26801V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26801V\"></sup>the court of the high priest,",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26802W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26802W\"></sup>but Peter was standing at the door outside. So the other disciple, who was known to the high priest, went out and spoke to the doorkeeper, and brought Peter in.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26803X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26803X\"></sup>Then the slave-girl who kept the door *said to Peter, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26803Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26803Y\"></sup>You are not also <i>one</i> of this man’s disciples, are you?” He *said, “I am not.”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Now the slaves and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26804Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26804Z\"></sup>officers were standing <i>there</i>, having made <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26804AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26804AA\"></sup>a charcoal fire, for it was cold and they were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26804AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26804AB\"></sup>warming themselves; and Peter was also with them, standing and warming himself.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26805AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26805AC\"></sup>The high priest then questioned Jesus about His disciples, and about His teaching.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Jesus answered him, <span class=\"woj\">“I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26806AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26806AD\"></sup>have spoken openly to the world; I always <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26806AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26806AE\"></sup>taught in synagogues and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26806AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26806AF\"></sup>in the temple, where all the Jews come together; and I spoke nothing in secret.</span>",
			"21": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Why do you question Me? Question those who have heard what I spoke to them; they know what I said.”</span>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>When He had said this, one of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26808AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26808AG\"></sup>officers standing nearby <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26808AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26808AH\"></sup>struck Jesus, saying, “Is that the way You answer the high priest?”",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26809AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26809AI\"></sup>Jesus answered him, <span class=\"woj\">“If I have spoken wrongly, testify of the wrong; but if rightly, why do you strike Me?”</span>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26810AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26810AJ\"></sup>So Annas sent Him bound to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26810AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26810AK\"></sup>Caiaphas the high priest.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26811AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26811AL\"></sup>Now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26811AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26811AM\"></sup>Simon Peter was standing and warming himself. So they said to him, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26811AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26811AN\"></sup>You are not also <i>one</i> of His disciples, are you?” He denied <i>it</i>, and said, “I am not.”",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>One of the slaves of the high priest, being a relative of the one <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26812AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26812AO\"></sup>whose ear Peter cut off, *said, “Did I not see you in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26812AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26812AP\"></sup>the garden with Him?”",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Peter then denied <i>it</i> again, and immediately <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26813AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26813AQ\"></sup>a rooster crowed.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26814AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26814AR\"></sup>Then they *led Jesus from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26814AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26814AS\"></sup>Caiaphas into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26814AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26814AT\"></sup>the Praetorium, and it was early; and they themselves did not enter into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26814AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26814AU\"></sup>the Praetorium so that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26814AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26814AV\"></sup>they would not be defiled, but might eat the Passover.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26815AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26815AW\"></sup>Therefore Pilate went out to them and *said, “What accusation do you bring against this Man?”",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>They answered and said to him, “If this Man were not an evildoer, we would not have delivered Him to you.”",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>So Pilate said to them, “Take Him yourselves, and judge Him according to your law.” The Jews said to him, “We are not permitted to put anyone to death,”",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>to fulfill <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26818AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26818AX\"></sup>the word of Jesus which He spoke, signifying by what kind of death He was about to die.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>Therefore Pilate <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26819AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26819AY\"></sup>entered again into the Praetorium, and summoned Jesus and said to Him, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26819AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26819AZ\"></sup>Are You the King of the Jews?”",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>Jesus answered, <span class=\"woj\">“Are you saying this on your own initiative, or did others tell you about Me?”</span>",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>Pilate answered, “I am not a Jew, am I? Your own nation and the chief priests delivered You to me; what have You done?”",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>Jesus answered, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26822BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26822BA\"></sup>My kingdom is not of this world. If My kingdom were of this world, then My servants would be fighting so that I would not be handed over to the Jews; but as it is, My kingdom is not of this realm.”</span>",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>Therefore Pilate said to Him, “So You are a king?” Jesus answered, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26823BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26823BB\"></sup>You say <i>correctly</i> that I am a king. For this I have been born, and for this I have come into the world, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26823BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26823BC\"></sup>to testify to the truth. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26823BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26823BD\"></sup>Everyone who is of the truth hears My voice.”</span>",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>Pilate *said to Him, “What is truth?”And when he had said this, he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26824BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26824BE\"></sup>went out again to the Jews and *said to them, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26824BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26824BF\"></sup>I find no guilt in Him.",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26825BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26825BG\"></sup>But you have a custom that I release someone for you at the Passover; do you wish then that I release for you the King of the Jews?”",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>So they cried out again, saying, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26826BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26826BH\"></sup>Not this Man, but Barabbas.” Now Barabbas was a robber."
		},
		"19": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">19 </span>Pilate then took Jesus and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26827A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26827A\"></sup>scourged Him.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26828B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26828B\"></sup>And the soldiers twisted together a crown of thorns and put it on His head, and put a purple robe on Him;",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>and they <i>began</i> to come up to Him and say, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26829C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26829C\"></sup>Hail, King of the Jews!” and to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26829D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26829D\"></sup>give Him slaps <i>in the face</i>.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Pilate <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26830E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26830E\"></sup>came out again and *said to them, “Behold, I am bringing Him out to you so that you may know that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26830F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26830F\"></sup>I find no guilt in Him.”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Jesus then came out, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26831G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26831G\"></sup>wearing the crown of thorns and the purple robe. <i>Pilate</i> *said to them, “Behold, the Man!”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>So when the chief priests and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26832H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26832H\"></sup>officers saw Him, they cried out saying, “Crucify, crucify!” Pilate *said to them, “Take Him yourselves and crucify Him, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26832I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26832I\"></sup>I find no guilt in Him.”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>The Jews answered him, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26833J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26833J\"></sup>We have a law, and by that law He ought to die because He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26833K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26833K\"></sup>made Himself out <i>to be</i> the Son of God.”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Therefore when Pilate heard this statement, he was <i>even</i> more afraid;",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>and he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26835L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26835L\"></sup>entered into the Praetorium again and *said to Jesus, “Where are You from?” But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26835M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26835M\"></sup>Jesus gave him no answer.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>So Pilate *said to Him, “You do not speak to me? Do You not know that I have authority to release You, and I have authority to crucify You?”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Jesus answered, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26837N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26837N\"></sup>You would have no authority over Me, unless it had been given you from above; for this reason <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26837O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26837O\"></sup>he who delivered Me to you has <i>the</i> greater sin.”</span>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>As a result of this Pilate made efforts to release Him, but the Jews cried out saying, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26838P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26838P\"></sup>If you release this Man, you are no friend of Caesar; everyone who makes himself out <i>to be</i> a king opposes Caesar.”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Therefore when Pilate heard these words, he brought Jesus out, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26839Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26839Q\"></sup>sat down on the judgment seat at a place called The Pavement, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26839R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26839R\"></sup>in Hebrew, Gabbatha.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Now it was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26840S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26840S\"></sup>the day of preparation for the Passover; it was about the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26840T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26840T\"></sup>sixth hour. And he *said to the Jews, “Behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26840U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26840U\"></sup>your King!”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>So they cried out, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26841V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26841V\"></sup>Away with <i>Him</i>, away with <i>Him</i>, crucify Him!” Pilate *said to them, “Shall I crucify your King?” The chief priests answered, “We have no king but Caesar.”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>So he then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26842W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26842W\"></sup>handed Him over to them to be crucified.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26843X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26843X\"></sup>They took Jesus, therefore, and He went out, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26843Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26843Y\"></sup>bearing His own cross, to the place called <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26843Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26843Z\"></sup>the Place of a Skull, which is called <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26843AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26843AA\"></sup>in Hebrew, Golgotha.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>There they crucified Him, and with Him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26844AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26844AB\"></sup>two other men, one on either side, and Jesus in between.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Pilate also wrote an inscription and put it on the cross. It was written, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26845AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26845AC\"></sup>JESUS THE NAZARENE, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26845AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26845AD\"></sup>THE KING OF THE JEWS.”",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Therefore many of the Jews read this inscription, for the place where Jesus was crucified was near the city; and it was written <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26846AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26846AE\"></sup>in Hebrew, Latin <i>and</i> in Greek.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>So the chief priests of the Jews were saying to Pilate, “Do not write, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26847AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26847AF\"></sup>The King of the Jews’; but that He said, ‘I am <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26847AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26847AG\"></sup>King of the Jews.’”",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Pilate answered, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26848AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26848AH\"></sup>What I have written I have written.”",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26849AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26849AI\"></sup>the soldiers, when they had crucified Jesus, took His outer garments and made <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26849AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26849AJ\"></sup>four parts, a part to every soldier and <i>also</i> the tunic; now the tunic was seamless, woven in one piece.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>So they said to one another, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26850AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26850AK\"></sup>Let us not tear it, but cast lots for it, <i>to decide</i> whose it shall be”; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26850AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26850AL\"></sup><i>this was</i> to fulfill the Scripture: “<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">They</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26850AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26850AM\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">divided My outer garments among them, and for My clothing they cast</span> <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">lots</span>.”",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Therefore the soldiers did these things.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26851AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26851AN\"></sup>But standing by the cross of Jesus were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26851AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26851AO\"></sup>His mother, and His mother’s sister, Mary the <i>wife</i> of Clopas, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26851AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26851AP\"></sup>Mary Magdalene.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>When Jesus then saw His mother, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26852AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26852AQ\"></sup>the disciple whom He loved standing nearby, He *said to His mother, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26852AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26852AR\"></sup>Woman, behold, your son!”</span>",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Then He *said to the disciple, <span class=\"woj\">“Behold, your mother!”</span> From that hour the disciple took her into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26853AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26853AS\"></sup>his own <i>household</i>.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>After this, Jesus, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26854AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26854AT\"></sup>knowing that all things had already been accomplished, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26854AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26854AU\"></sup>to fulfill the Scripture, *said, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26854AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26854AV\"></sup>I am thirsty.”</span>",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>A jar full of sour wine was standing there; so <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26855AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26855AW\"></sup>they put a sponge full of the sour wine upon <i>a branch of</i> hyssop and brought it up to His mouth.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>Therefore when Jesus had received the sour wine, He said, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26856AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26856AX\"></sup>It is finished!”</span> And He bowed His head and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26856AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26856AY\"></sup>gave up His spirit.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>Then the Jews, because it was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26857AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26857AZ\"></sup>the day of preparation, so that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26857BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26857BA\"></sup>the bodies would not remain on the cross on the Sabbath (for that Sabbath was a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26857BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26857BB\"></sup>high day), asked Pilate that their legs might be broken, and <i>that</i> they might be taken away.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>So the soldiers came, and broke the legs of the first man and of the other who was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26858BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26858BC\"></sup>crucified with Him;",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>but coming to Jesus, when they saw that He was already dead, they did not break His legs.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>But one of the soldiers pierced His side with a spear, and immediately <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26860BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26860BD\"></sup>blood and water came out.",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>And he who has seen has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26861BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26861BE\"></sup>testified, and his testimony is true; and he knows that he is telling the truth, so that you also may believe.",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>For these things came to pass <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26862BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26862BF\"></sup>to fulfill the Scripture, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26862BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26862BG\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Not a bone of Him shall be</span> <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">broken</span>.”",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>And again another Scripture says, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26863BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26863BH\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">They shall look on Him whom they pierced</span>.”",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26864BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26864BI\"></sup>After these things Joseph of Arimathea, being a disciple of Jesus, but a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26864BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26864BJ\"></sup>secret <i>one</i> for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26864BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26864BK\"></sup>fear of the Jews, asked Pilate that he might take away the body of Jesus; and Pilate granted permission. So he came and took away His body.",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26865BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26865BL\"></sup>Nicodemus, who had first come to Him by night, also came, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26865BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26865BM\"></sup>bringing a mixture of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26865BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26865BN\"></sup>myrrh and aloes, about a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26865BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26865BO\"></sup>hundred pounds <i>weight</i>.",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>So they took the body of Jesus and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26866BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26866BP\"></sup>bound it in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26866BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26866BQ\"></sup>linen wrappings with the spices, as is the burial custom of the Jews.",
			"41": "<sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup>Now in the place where He was crucified there was a garden, and in the garden a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26867BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26867BR\"></sup>new tomb <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26867BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26867BS\"></sup>in which no one had yet been laid.",
			"42": "<sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup>Therefore because of the Jewish day of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26868BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26868BT\"></sup>preparation, since the tomb was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26868BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26868BU\"></sup>nearby, they laid Jesus there."
		},
		"20": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">20 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26869A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26869A\"></sup>Now on the first <i>day</i> of the week <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26869B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26869B\"></sup>Mary Magdalene *came early to the tomb, while it *was still dark, and *saw <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26869C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26869C\"></sup>the stone <i>already</i> taken away from the tomb.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>So she *ran and *came to Simon Peter and to the other <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26870D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26870D\"></sup>disciple whom Jesus loved, and *said to them, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26870E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26870E\"></sup>They have taken away the Lord out of the tomb, and we do not know where they have laid Him.”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26871F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26871F\"></sup>So Peter and the other disciple went forth, and they were going to the tomb.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>The two were running together; and the other disciple ran ahead faster than Peter and came to the tomb first;",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26873G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26873G\"></sup>stooping and looking in, he *saw the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26873H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26873H\"></sup>linen wrappings lying <i>there</i>; but he did not go in.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>And so Simon Peter also *came, following him, and entered the tomb; and he *saw the linen wrappings lying <i>there</i>,",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26875I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26875I\"></sup>the face-cloth which had been on His head, not lying with the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26875J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26875J\"></sup>linen wrappings, but rolled up in a place by itself.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>So the other disciple who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26876K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26876K\"></sup>had first come to the tomb then also entered, and he saw and believed.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>For as yet <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26877L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26877L\"></sup>they did not understand the Scripture, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26877M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26877M\"></sup>that He must rise again from the dead.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>So the disciples went away again <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26878N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26878N\"></sup>to their own homes.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26879O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26879O\"></sup>But Mary was standing outside the tomb weeping; and so, as she wept, she <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26879P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26879P\"></sup>stooped and looked into the tomb;",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>and she *saw <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26880Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26880Q\"></sup>two angels in white sitting, one at the head and one at the feet, where the body of Jesus had been lying.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>And they *said to her, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26881R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26881R\"></sup>Woman, why are you weeping?” She *said to them, “Because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26881S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26881S\"></sup>they have taken away my Lord, and I do not know where they have laid Him.”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>When she had said this, she turned around and *<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26882T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26882T\"></sup>saw Jesus standing <i>there</i>, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26882U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26882U\"></sup>did not know that it was Jesus.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Jesus *said to her, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26883V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26883V\"></sup>Woman, why are you weeping? Whom are you seeking?”</span> Supposing Him to be the gardener, she *said to Him, “Sir, if you have carried Him away, tell me where you have laid Him, and I will take Him away.”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Jesus *said to her, <span class=\"woj\">“Mary!”</span> She turned and *said to Him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26884W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26884W\"></sup>in Hebrew, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26884X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26884X\"></sup>Rabboni!” (which means, Teacher).",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Jesus *said to her, <span class=\"woj\">“Stop clinging to Me, for I have not yet ascended to the Father; but go to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26885Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26885Y\"></sup>My brethren and say to them, ‘I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26885Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26885Z\"></sup>ascend to My Father and your Father, and My God and your God.’”</span>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26886AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26886AA\"></sup>Mary Magdalene *came, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26886AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26886AB\"></sup>announcing to the disciples, “I have seen the Lord,” and <i>that</i> He had said these things to her.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>So when it was evening on that day, the first <i>day</i> of the week, and when the doors were shut where the disciples were, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26887AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26887AC\"></sup>fear of the Jews, Jesus came and stood in their midst and *said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26887AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26887AD\"></sup>Peace <i>be</i> with you.”</span>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>And when He had said this, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26888AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26888AE\"></sup>He showed them both His hands and His side. The disciples then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26888AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26888AF\"></sup>rejoiced when they saw the Lord.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>So Jesus said to them again, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26889AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26889AG\"></sup>Peace <i>be</i> with you; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26889AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26889AH\"></sup>as the Father has sent Me, I also send you.”</span>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>And when He had said this, He breathed on them and *said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Receive the Holy Spirit.</span>",
			"23": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26891AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26891AI\"></sup>If you forgive the sins of any, <i>their sins</i> have been forgiven them; if you retain the <i>sins</i> of any, they have been retained.”</span>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26892AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26892AJ\"></sup>Thomas, one of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26892AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26892AK\"></sup>the twelve, called <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26892AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26892AL\"></sup>Didymus, was not with them when Jesus came.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>So the other disciples were saying to him, “We have seen the Lord!” But he said to them, “Unless I see in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26893AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26893AM\"></sup>His hands the imprint of the nails, and put my finger into the place of the nails, and put my hand into His side, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26893AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26893AN\"></sup>I will not believe.”",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>After eight days His disciples were again inside, and Thomas with them. Jesus *came, the doors having been shut, and stood in their midst and said, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26894AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26894AO\"></sup>Peace <i>be</i> with you.”</span>",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Then He *said to Thomas, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26895AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26895AP\"></sup>Reach here with your finger, and see My hands; and reach here your hand and put it into My side; and do not be unbelieving, but believing.”</span>",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Thomas answered and said to Him, “My Lord and my God!”",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>Jesus *said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“Because you have seen Me, have you believed? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26897AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26897AQ\"></sup>Blessed <i>are</i> they who did not see, and <i>yet</i> believed.”</span>",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26898AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26898AR\"></sup>Therefore many other <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26898AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26898AS\"></sup>signs Jesus also performed in the presence of the disciples, which are not written in this book;",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>but these have been written <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26899AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26899AT\"></sup>so that you may believe that Jesus is the Christ, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26899AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26899AU\"></sup>the Son of God; and that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26899AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26899AV\"></sup>believing you may have life in His name."
		},
		"21": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">21 </span>After these things Jesus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26900A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26900A\"></sup>manifested Himself <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26900B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26900B\"></sup>again to the disciples at the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26900C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26900C\"></sup>Sea of Tiberias, and He manifested <i>Himself</i> in this way.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Simon Peter, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26901D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26901D\"></sup>Thomas called Didymus, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26901E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26901E\"></sup>Nathanael of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26901F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26901F\"></sup>Cana in Galilee, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26901G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26901G\"></sup>the <i>sons</i> of Zebedee, and two others of His disciples were together.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Simon Peter *said to them, “I am going fishing.” They *said to him, “We will also come with you.” They went out and got into the boat; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26902H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26902H\"></sup>that night they caught nothing.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>But when the day was now breaking, Jesus stood on the beach; yet the disciples did not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26903I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26903I\"></sup>know that it was Jesus.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>So Jesus *said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Children, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26904J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26904J\"></sup>you do not have any fish, do you?”</span> They answered Him, “No.”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>And He said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26905K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26905K\"></sup>Cast the net on the right-hand side of the boat and you will find <i>a catch</i>.”</span> So they cast, and then they were not able to haul it in because of the great number of fish.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26906L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26906L\"></sup>Therefore that disciple whom Jesus loved *said to Peter, “It is the Lord.” So when Simon Peter heard that it was the Lord, he put his outer garment on (for he was stripped <i>for work</i>), and threw himself into the sea.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>But the other disciples came in the little boat, for they were not far from the land, but about one hundred yards away, dragging the net <i>full</i> of fish.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>So when they got out on the land, they *saw a charcoal <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26908M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26908M\"></sup>fire <i>already</i> laid and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26908N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26908N\"></sup>fish placed on it, and bread.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Jesus *said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Bring some of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26909O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26909O\"></sup>fish which you have now caught.”</span>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Simon Peter went up and drew the net to land, full of large fish, a hundred and fifty-three; and although there were so many, the net was not torn.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Jesus *said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Come <i>and</i> have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26911P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26911P\"></sup>breakfast.”</span> None of the disciples ventured to question Him, “Who are You?” knowing that it was the Lord.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Jesus *came and *took <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26912Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26912Q\"></sup>the bread and *gave <i>it</i> to them, and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26912R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26912R\"></sup>fish likewise.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>This is now the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26913S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26913S\"></sup>third time that Jesus was manifested to the disciples, after He was raised from the dead.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>So when they had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26914T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26914T\"></sup>finished breakfast, Jesus *said to Simon Peter, <span class=\"woj\">“Simon, <i>son</i> of John, do you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26914U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26914U\"></sup>love Me more than these?”</span> He *said to Him, “Yes, Lord; You know that I love You.” He *said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“Tend <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26914V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26914V\"></sup>My lambs.”</span>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>He *said to him again a second time, <span class=\"woj\">“Simon, <i>son</i> of John, do you love Me?”</span> He *said to Him, “Yes, Lord; You know that I love You.” He *said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26915W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26915W\"></sup>Shepherd My sheep.”</span>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>He *said to him the third time, <span class=\"woj\">“Simon, <i>son</i> of John, do you love Me?”</span> Peter was grieved because He said to him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26916X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26916X\"></sup>the third time, <span class=\"woj\">“Do you love Me?”</span> And he said to Him, “Lord, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26916Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26916Y\"></sup>You know all things; You know that I love You.” Jesus *said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26916Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26916Z\"></sup>Tend My sheep.</span>",
			"18": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Truly, truly, I say to you, when you were younger, you used to gird yourself and walk wherever you wished; but when you grow old, you will stretch out your hands and someone else will gird you, and bring you where you do not wish to <i>go</i>.”</span>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Now this He said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26918AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26918AA\"></sup>signifying by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26918AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26918AB\"></sup>what kind of death he would glorify God. And when He had spoken this, He *said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26918AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26918AC\"></sup>Follow Me!”</span>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Peter, turning around, *saw the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26919AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26919AD\"></sup>disciple whom Jesus loved following <i>them</i>; the one who also had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26919AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26919AE\"></sup>leaned back on His bosom at the supper and said, “Lord, who is the one who betrays You?”",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>So Peter seeing him *said to Jesus, “Lord, and what about this man?”",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Jesus *said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“If I want him to remain <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26921AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26921AF\"></sup>until I come, what <i>is that</i> to you? You <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26921AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26921AG\"></sup>follow Me!”</span>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Therefore this saying went out among <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26922AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26922AH\"></sup>the brethren that that disciple would not die; yet Jesus did not say to him that he would not die, but <i>only</i>, <span class=\"woj\">“If I want him to remain <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26922AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26922AI\"></sup>until I come, what <i>is that</i> to you?”</span>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>This is the disciple who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26923AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26923AJ\"></sup>is testifying to these things and wrote these things, and we know that his testimony is true.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>And there are also <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-26924AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-26924AK\"></sup>many other things which Jesus did, which if they *were written in detail, I suppose that even the world itself *would not contain the books that *would be written."
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;